\":\"earth\",\"likes\":250,\"dislikes\":18},{\"id\":112,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Cancer and Capricorn form the connection of the \\\"family-career.\\\" If home and comfort are important for the first one, for the other one, work and social status are in privileges. Cancer is a romantic by nature: he loves nature, is inspired by art, and is attentive to people around him. He may not understand the cold behavior of Capricorn, who also seems to be more practical. However, even such relations have a future, if the zones of influence in the pair are correctly divided.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":391,\"dislikes\":53},{\"id\":113,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Aquarians are friendly and nice people with a fine mental organization. They have a lively mind and curiosity. Representatives of this zodiac sign easily make new acquaintances, share their original ideas about the world, and they are not afraid to change their usual way of life. They hate the dullness and routine. Aquarius is easily impressed by air signs: it will chat non-stop with Gemini and try to spend as much time as possible with Libra. And it will find another soul mate in an independent and confident Sagittarius.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\",\"libra\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":820,\"dislikes\":89},{\"id\":114,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Aquarius\",\"description\":\"Representatives of the air element – Gemini and Aquarius – understand each other perfectly. This union is built on an incredibly emotional and spiritual connection. From the side, their relationships seem almost mystical, because no one can understand them.\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":643,\"dislikes\":107},{\"id\":115,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>If Aquarius wants to be with someone who really understands this sing, then it needs to turn to the air zodiac signs. The most ideal option is Gemini, with whom Aquarius can count on deep feelings and devotion. Also, Aquarius easily finds many things in common with Sagittarius, as they can share a passion for new adventures. </p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":529,\"dislikes\":54},{\"id\":118,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The element of Air is considered to be the trigon of ideas and intelligence. People who belong to this element are constantly in search of new knowledge and sensations. The element of Air carries in itself a changing creative activity, giving to people such qualities as flexibility, liveliness, mobility of the mind and psycho, and insatiability. They do not like monotony since it depresses their psycho. The basic principles of a trigon are interconnection and exchange.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"gemini\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":301,\"dislikes\":15},{\"id\":119,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Aquarius love to have an active social life, but they see it differently. Together these zodiac signs make up the balance \\\"personality-community.\\\" Creative self-expression and the ability to show oneself are important for Leo, and Aquarius values freedom and society of equals. Mutual understanding does not immediately arise in this couple, but the passion for parties and events becomes a unifying factor.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"leo\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":468,\"dislikes\":78},{\"id\":120,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Sentimental Pisces are looking for a man who will become their soul mate. And they can build trustful and deep relationships with representatives of two elements: Water and Earth. Since Pisces themselves often soar in the clouds and dream a lot, they need a more practical and down to earth partner. Sagittarius is perfect for this role: he knows a lot about romance, but he is not far away from reality.\\r\\n\\r\\nPisces can have an unusually harmonious relationship with Capricorn. Usually, a spark appears between the representatives of these signs, which forces them to develop communication a lot. The same powerful connection is formed with Cancer: partners literally read each other's thoughts and desires.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"cancer\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":620,\"dislikes\":131},{\"id\":121,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Pisces \",\"description\":\"<p>There is an instant attraction between Cancer and Pisces. Deep mental communication is not easy to eliminate, so these relationships can last a very long time. The fact that both zodiac signs belong to the water element determines the similarity of interests, values, and aspirations. </p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":717,\"dislikes\":97},{\"id\":122,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Natural compatibility is within its element of water: with Cancer and Scorpio. Successful relationships: trust, mutual understanding, spiritual closeness.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":527,\"dislikes\":58},{\"id\":123,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>Water is considered the trigon of sensations and feelings. Representatives of the water element have a strong connection with the unconscious mind. They are not interested in empty talking, which doesn’t have spiritual intimacy and sincerity. People in whose horoscopes this element is expressed have inner power, imaginative thinking, and sensitivity. When a whole emotional storm occurs inside them, they don’t show it outside. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe people of the Water Trigon do not forget to take care of themselves and their loved ones. They value family values and comfort. Their power is to contact the outside world, and their weakness is excessive impressionability and spiritual instability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":321,\"dislikes\":21},{\"id\":124,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Mutual understanding in such a couple does not come immediately. Spirituality and inner experiences are important for Pisces, while the Virgo is responsible for practical and rational decisions. Their interests lie in different spheres, which can become an obstacle to creating strong relations.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"virgo\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":412,\"dislikes\":64}]"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:48:37.781Z"
      },
      {
        "_connectionId": "6013",
        "cache": {},
        "request": {
          "method": "GET",
