          ],
          "content": {
            "size": 53648,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":165,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":6648,\"dislikes\":235,\"order\":3,\"text\":\"<p>This is the hard time for you energetically wise. Keep physical activity a minimum, be kind and understanding to yourself. Extra carefulness in everything you do is a must.</p>\"},{\"id\":210,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":6791,\"dislikes\":229,\"order\":3,\"text\":\"<p>This is the lowest time of your mental activity. So don't rush, don't take risks, don't make important decisions. Try to calm down and go with the flow for now.</p>\"},{\"id\":257,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":7055,\"dislikes\":321,\"order\":3,\"text\":\"The bottom of your emotional phase may feel like a desert that you are lost in. Just make even little steps away from feeling awful and soon they will lead you somewhere.\"},{\"id\":164,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3779,\"dislikes\":138,\"order\":6,\"text\":\"<p>Your energy is at its lowest, so try to keep up with only essential duties and provide yourself with plenty of rest.</p>\"},{\"id\":209,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2379,\"dislikes\":43,\"order\":6,\"text\":\"Plenty of rest is a must for you right now, especially rest for your mind. So don't get involved into stressful or risky situations, instead spend some time with your friends or have a nice 'you' day.\"},{\"id\":256,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":6,\"text\":\"<p>You might have the sense of hatred towards the others. Remember, it doesn't define you as a mean person. You're just in a bad place right now. It will pass.</p>\"},{\"id\":60,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":112,\"dislikes\":11,\"order\":9,\"text\":\"<p>You are at the very bottom of your physical activity cycle. If you do not support the body during this period, health problems are possible. Avoid unnecessary stress: even keep your sex life to a minimum.</p>\"},{\"id\":75,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":61,\"dislikes\":6,\"order\":9,\"text\":\"<p>You are at the peak of the \\\"reboot\\\": you encapsulate, transform into a pupa, from which a butterfly will soon fly out. This is the best time for communication with yourself, introspection and resolution of internal conflicts.</p>\"},{\"id\":105,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2260,\"dislikes\":62,\"order\":9,\"text\":\"<p>Your mind is resting, and you should not interfere with it: during this period, engage in creativity, communication with friends, sports, go to the cinema for a comedy or take a walk in the park. After rebooting, your intelligence will work with renewed vigor.</p>\"},{\"id\":163,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":4097,\"dislikes\":97,\"order\":12,\"text\":\"<p>You are out of breath and you should just take it as it is for now. Pay a lot of attention to your sleep, keep meals healthy and nutritious and try to stay away from any sources of stress.</p>\"},{\"id\":208,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":12,\"text\":\"<p>Do not expect any high results from yourself at the moment. The best thing you can do for yourself is to rest and spend your time with the people who love you.</p>\"},{\"id\":255,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":6469,\"dislikes\":509,\"order\":12,\"text\":\"<p>The darkness in your mind is pushing you to conceive negatively, and you have gone deep into it. Now, you are in a position, where you can't find anybody around you, and are lost in your own deep thoughts. But remember, you are NOT alone.</p>\"},{\"id\":162,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":15,\"text\":\"<p>Keep it as comfy and peaceful as you can. You shouldn't get involved into the activities that require too much of endurance, concentration and power.</p>\"},{\"id\":207,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2395,\"dislikes\":88,\"order\":15,\"text\":\"<p>You controlled your temper when that certain someone tried to push your buttons, but it's harder for you now to think clearly and make well-thought decisions. So try to avoid arguments.</p>\"},{\"id\":254,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":15,\"text\":\"<p>You may find it difficult to stay active and motivated now, which is absolutely normal. Do what you can and don't expect more from yourself.</p>\"},{\"id\":161,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3094,\"dislikes\":85,\"order\":18,\"text\":\"<p>This is the time for relaxation and contemplation. Avoid stress and extra work. If someone can give you a hand with your daily tasks, kindly ask for it.</p>\"},{\"id\":206,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":18,\"text\":\"<p>In the next days, you have a higher chance of getting sick, especially if you concentrate on your problems, mistakes and other complications. Try to avoid overthinking your troubles.</p>\"},{\"id\":253,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":18,\"text\":\"<p>Try to find inspiration in everything you do. It will help you through the rough time like this.</p>\"},{\"id\":59,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":71,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":21,\"text\":\"<p>The peak of the negative phase of physical activity is approaching: it is difficult for you to wake up in the morning, and in the evening you fall off your feet. Carrying out routine duties requires maximum concentration. Possibly feeling unwell.<span></span></p>\"},{\"id\":74,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":46,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":21,\"text\":\"<p>The peak of the \\\"reboot\\\" phase is approaching, the need for privacy and silence is growing. If you do not have enough personal space, go for a walk in a secluded place: in a park, on the shore of a reservoir, in the historical part of the city.</p>\"},{\"id\":104,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1841,\"dislikes\":111,\"order\":21,\"text\":\"<p>The need for informational silence is growing. It seems that the mind is inactive, but during this period it assimilates previously obtained information.</p>\"},{\"id\":160,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":24,\"text\":\"<p>Treat yourself with a day-off or at least an evening for yourself when you can relax the way you prefer and recharge your batteries. Keep your physical activity low, instead give your body lots of love by taking a long nice bath or getting a massage.</p>\"},{\"id\":205,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1968,\"dislikes\":158,\"order\":24,\"text\":\"<p>Some negative thoughts about your co-workers can annoy you today. Remember, that it's just the effect of the phase you are in.</p>\"},{\"id\":252,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4982,\"dislikes\":155,\"order\":24,\"text\":\"<p>If you manage to keep your range of emotions under control these days, you are already a winner.</p>\"},{\"id\":159,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3282,\"dislikes\":121,\"order\":27,\"text\":\"<p>Don't expect form yourself too much, it's too hard for you to keep up with all the duties. Prioritize and do only the important ones.</p>\"},{\"id\":204,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":27,\"text\":\"Even simple tasks at work can easily wear you out today. It may frustrate you to a large extent, but you need to be strong.\"},{\"id\":251,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":27,\"text\":\"<p>It's not easy to stay positive these days. Don't be so hard on yourself for not being cheerful and enthusiastic.</p>\"},{\"id\":58,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":18,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":30,\"text\":\"<p>Avoid overloading, even if you are not engaged in manual labor. During this period, it will be difficult for you to do the most ordinary work, not to mention overtime. In household chores, also avoid fanaticism - it is better to postpone cleaning for a few days.</p>\"},{\"id\":73,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":50,\"dislikes\":4,\"order\":30,\"text\":\"<p>Avoid emotional overload, conflict, difficult conversations. At this time, it is difficult for you to even maintain communication – sharp outbursts of emotions are undesirable. Put aside aesthetic experimentation – you are not too receptive to new things right now.</p>\"},{\"id\":106,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":14,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":30,\"text\":\"<p>Try not to overload yourself with intellectual work: at best, you will have to look for mistakes and redo, at worst, the consequences can be irreversible.</p>\"},{\"id\":203,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1926,\"dislikes\":78,\"order\":33,\"text\":\"<p>Since your intellectual biorhythm phase is low, you'd better keep aside from investing money or making expensive purchases right now.</p>\"},{\"id\":250,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":33,\"text\":\"<p>Excess of enthusiasm is not satisfying for you at the moment. Things can also go against you. Don't get extremely excited.</p>\"},{\"id\":158,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":36,\"text\":\"<p>You are it the negative phase of strength and energy, so it's better not to start any ambitious projects at work or do heavy workouts. Moderation and good rest should be your priorities now.</p>\"},{\"id\":202,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":36,\"text\":\"<p>Your research project is not going to succeed if you are planning to begin with it, and can give you a massive loss. Today is not a favorable day to start something ambitious.</p>\"},{\"id\":249,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":36,\"text\":\"<p>Your mood is running here and there today. If you can't help it, try to interact with people less.</p>\"},{\"id\":11,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":49,\"dislikes\":12,\"order\":39,\"text\":\"<p>In the negative phase, you may feel a decline in physical strength. In the morning, you have to fight with the desire to stay in bed, and after lunch with drowsiness. Lack of energy will decrease sexual activity. Do not overload yourself with work. Rest to restore strength.</p>\"},{\"id\":17,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4761,\"dislikes\":190,\"order\":39,\"text\":\"<p>The emotional biorhythm will enter a negative phase. You might be feeling utterly devastated and worthless. The mood will frequently be changing throughout the day. Try to avoid stressful situations, get more rest, and treat yourself.</p>\"},{\"id\":25,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1957,\"dislikes\":70,\"order\":39,\"text\":\"<p>The intellectual biorhythm is going through a decline phase. It’s better to postpone any serious work and making important decisions. Any mental activity will seem tiring and boring. Concentrating on specific tasks will require all your efforts.</p>\"},{\"id\":157,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2806,\"dislikes\":102,\"order\":42,\"text\":\"<p>Any spa activities are highly recommended now, so go and treat yourself. Don't forget to have a good long nigh sleep after.<span></span></p>\"},{\"id\":201,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":42,\"text\":\"You are swayed by analytical minds today. You want logic and reason to guide you, but you experience hard time using them right. It's better to postpone some analytical tasks if possible.\"},{\"id\":248,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":42,\"text\":\"<p>Your contradictory thinking while having a conversation with others can bring you only to misunderstanding. You'd better postpone some serious talks for later.</p>\"},{\"id\":156,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":45,\"text\":\"<p>The best thing for you right now is to go with a flow and not try to achieve anything more than you can by doing regular daily task. The time to act will come, but now it's better to keep calm and be gentle with yourself.</p>\"},{\"id\":200,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1929,\"dislikes\":78,\"order\":45,\"text\":\"<p>You may face numerous obstacles in the coming days, especially considering your struggle to concentrate and proceed information right now. It is a time to think immensely and deal with the situation you are going to face.</p>\"},{\"id\":247,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":45,\"text\":\"<p>If you feel like some of your family members treats you the way which you don't deserve, try to see the situation from their point of view as well. You may have a tendency to get this all wrong due to your shaky emotional state now.</p>\"},{\"id\":155,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":48,\"text\":\"<p>Make sure you don't overload yourself with work these days. You shouldn't reach your energy limit, because if you wear yourself out completely, it will take you a very long time to recover.</p>\"},{\"id\":199,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":48,\"text\":\"<p>There is a chance that you have a difference of opinion with someone today. Remember that it's a dangerous time to have arguments right now. Not only it's going to be tough for you to stand your ground, you can easily hurt somebody with a careless word.</p>\"},{\"id\":246,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":48,\"text\":\"Try not to spoil your family's life because of your current short-tempered state of mind. If you feel that your emotions are taking over you, take a couple of deep breaths and withdraw.\"},{\"id\":8,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":57,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":51,\"text\":\"<p>The biorhythm has passed the negative phase’s minimum. The mood is running hot and cold, so any remark or criticism may throw you off balance. Try to stay calm and self-confident and put any important matters off.</p>\"},{\"id\":57,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3497,\"dislikes\":87,\"order\":51,\"text\":\"<p>It's time to take care of your health – physical decline is fraught with \\\"holes\\\" in the immune system. Avoid heavy and spicy foods in favor of superfoods that contain trace elements and vitamins. Don't spur yourself on drinks that contain caffeine, as this will deplete your reserves of physical energy. Give preference to juices and herbal teas.</p>\"},{\"id\":102,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":32,\"dislikes\":4,\"order\":51,\"text\":\"<p>Forgetfulness is growing: the brain is tired and requires unloading. Take care of physical activities: work in the country, do the cleaning, cook a delicious dinner. Do something with your own hands or try to \\\"escape\\\" from information noise to nature.</p>\"},{\"id\":154,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":54,\"text\":\"It's crucial to watch your diet now. Focus on eating healthy and nutritious food to gain energy from it since you're in energetically low mode. Keep physical activity mild, but at least go out once a day for a short relaxing walk<span></span>\"},{\"id\":198,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1762,\"dislikes\":92,\"order\":54,\"text\":\"<p>If you are feeling more introverted than usual, this could be a little bit challenging. You will not feel comfortable while networking, and this may lead to a bit of disappointment.</p>\"},{\"id\":245,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":54,\"text\":\"<p>Don't get frustrated if your matchmaking efforts haven't gone the way you want. You can't force feelings that don't exist. If you let your ego get caught up in the lives of other people, you are really asking for trouble.</p>\"},{\"id\":153,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":57,\"text\":\"It's time for taking good care of yourself. Go have some air, do mild stretching, check your health and go to bed earlier. Such simple things will help you stay positive even in this negative physical phase<span></span>\"},{\"id\":197,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":57,\"text\":\"<p>Since it's getting harder for you to think through what you're saying, you may accidentally say something you didn't mean and then regret it. So try to stay still and interact with people less.</p>\"},{\"id\":244,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4398,\"dislikes\":146,\"order\":57,\"text\":\"Today your mind is in a firing state, which may give a deep wound to the people around you. Try not to get into disputes.\"},{\"id\":24,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":17,\"dislikes\":4,\"order\":60,\"text\":\"<p>The negative phase leads to a slowdown of mental activity. Your perception dulls, it’s getting harder to concentrate and to absorb new information. Try to avoid complicated tasks and not to make significant decisions.</p>\"},{\"id\":56,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":60,\"text\":\"<p>Physical energy decreases: do not plan long trips, training and seminars, as well as business meetings during this time. Your energy is not enough right now to achieve good results – you will only wear yourself out uselessly.</p>\"},{\"id\":72,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":60,\"text\":\"<p>Time to devote time to personal aesthetic and spiritual needs: to be alone with nature, read your favorite author, listen to music. In the phase of emotional decline, you are less productive creatively, but this does not prevent you from receiving aesthetic pleasure.</p>\"},{\"id\":152,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3637,\"dislikes\":112,\"order\":63,\"text\":\"<p>You are close to your lowest physical biorhythm phase, so don't be hard on yourself for not wanting or not doing something. Do only the essentials and rest as much as possible.</p>\"},{\"id\":196,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1864,\"dislikes\":62,\"order\":63,\"text\":\"<p>Sometimes it takes us more time to do even simple tasks. Just take it as it is right now and consider this while making a daily to do list.</p>\"},{\"id\":243,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":63,\"text\":\"<p>Be gentle with your feelings, especially negative ones. Accept them, but then try to change your mindset.</p>\"},{\"id\":151,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":66,\"text\":\"<p>Find pleasure in simple things which don't require lots of preparation and efforts, like spending time indoors with your family.</p>\"},{\"id\":195,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":66,\"text\":\"<p>Be gentle and understanding with yourself these days since your intellectual phase is not at its peak. We all make mistakes sometimes.</p>\"},{\"id\":242,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":66,\"text\":\"The permanence of empathy in you makes you a great person. But in the times like these it's better to be kind and supportive to yourself first.\"},{\"id\":55,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":32,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":69,\"text\":\"<p>It's time for rest and recovery. Healthy sleep, light healthy food, vitamins and fresh air are optimal.</p>\"},{\"id\":71,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":69,\"text\":\"<p>Your creativity diminishes, as does your need for communication. At this time, avoid imposed situations of communication – not very close people will not understand why you are less open than usual, and attempts to \\\"get into the soul\\\" will be annoying.</p>\"},{\"id\":101,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":21,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":69,\"text\":\"<p>Your intellectual potential is shrinking – your brain also needs to rest periodically. Try to avoid information overload: you simply will not perceive half of the information, and you will forget another part. Not the best period for trainings, conferences and seminars.</p>\"},{\"id\":150,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":72,\"text\":\"<p>Find time to do something that helps you gain energy but not waste it. Some help from you nearest and dearest with household chores and free time activities is highly welcome.</p>\"},{\"id\":194,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2436,\"dislikes\":105,\"order\":72,\"text\":\"<p>Your luck is not with you at the moment as you are continuously facing losses and troubles. Don't worry, this will pass, especially if you change your mindset and try to see the silver lining of everything that's happening.</p>\"},{\"id\":241,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":72,\"text\":\"<p>It is great that you are showing sympathy towards your close ones. But the excess of everything is good neither for them, nor for you.</p>\"},{\"id\":149,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3037,\"dislikes\":107,\"order\":75,\"text\":\"<p>Your strength and reaction is on its low, so try not to overload yourself with lots of tasks at work or at home. Otherwise you may be careless, make mistakes and you'll end up redoing them over and over again.</p>\"},{\"id\":193,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":75,\"text\":\"<p>While entering your house today, take care of leaving all work problems behind the door. Otherwise they'll spoil your mood and the entire evening.</p>\"},{\"id\":240,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":75,\"text\":\"<p>The infatuation towards someone can let you down strikingly. Kindly stay away from giving yourself up for the sake of someone else.</p>\"},{\"id\":148,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":78,\"text\":\"<p>The best thing you can do for yourself right now is to be gentle, understanding and supportive to your body limits and energy decrease you experience. Try to find the activity that helps you relax your mind and body.</p>\"},{\"id\":192,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":78,\"text\":\"<p>Your creative and inquisitive mind is lacking energy at the moment, but you can boost it with some entertaining rest, especially if any kind of art is included.</p>\"},{\"id\":239,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4346,\"dislikes\":112,\"order\":78,\"text\":\"<p>With a mindset full of creative and innovative ideas, you have the possibility to create something stunning. The main obstacle to that may be your self-doubt only.</p>\"},{\"id\":54,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":32,\"dislikes\":1,\"order\":81,\"text\":\"<p>A decline in energy puts the body into an economical mode: you want to sleep longer and need more time to prepare for a new day. If this period falls on a weekend, it is better to spend it in a relaxed mode. A book or movie should be preferred to outdoor activities.</p>\"},{\"id\":70,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":54,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":81,\"text\":\"<p>Time to prepare for an emotional reboot. Limit your social circle to the closest people. Take a break from social and creative activities.</p>\"},{\"id\":100,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1795,\"dislikes\":56,\"order\":81,\"text\":\"<p>During this period, avoid solving problems that require intellectual stress. Dedicate yourself, if possible, to routine or physical labor.</p>\"},{\"id\":238,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":84,\"text\":\"<p>Ups and downs have come your way in a very gentle manner and deeply diverted your mind, but now it is time for them to go. Focus on yourself and the feeling of presence here and now.</p>\"},{\"id\":237,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":87,\"text\":\"<p>Avoid people that make you anxious. Savor every single minute of your life. You will attain the goals which you have set in your mind very soon with your positive approach.</p>\"},{\"id\":53,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":22,\"dislikes\":1,\"order\":90,\"text\":\"<p>The critical phase of the physical biorhythm is the transition from the \\\"charged battery\\\" state to the \\\"squeezed lemon\\\" state. On the \\\"critical days\\\" of the physical cycle, everything falls out of your hands, your reaction worsens, clumsiness appears, which is fraught with injuries and bruises. Be careful while exercising and walking.</p>\"},{\"id\":69,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":90,\"text\":\"<p>The phase of emotional restraint begins. Outbursts of emotions, and not always positive ones, which preceded this period, make you \\\"freeze the moment\\\" in order to safely \\\"reboot\\\" in the next phase.</p>\"},{\"id\":99,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":21,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":90,\"text\":\"<p>Reduced attentiveness and concentration, reduced working capacity. It is difficult for you to tune in to solving current problems, and when you get down to business, it moves slowly and with minimal productivity.</p>\"},{\"id\":147,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2675,\"dislikes\":70,\"order\":93,\"text\":\"<p>Take it easy and choose the kind of activity you are familiar with and which brings you satisfaction. Even if it's just going for a walk.</p>\"},{\"id\":191,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":93,\"text\":\"<p>Your popularity, which has taken the hearts of many people around the globe, is definitely your strong suit, use it.</p>\"},{\"id\":236,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":93,\"text\":\"<p>Your dramatic feelings will profoundly push you to take part in some drama today, but you'd better fight this urge.</p>\"},{\"id\":146,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":96,\"text\":\"<p>The lack of energy and motivation is temporary, so don't you worry about not doing your best training or doing your household duties. Moderate yoga practice and meditation is the best choice for you right now.</p>\"},{\"id\":190,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1326,\"dislikes\":157,\"order\":96,\"text\":\"<p>The agendas which you are going to show in your project meeting today may be useful for some people, and some will dislike it. Do not lose hope as it is a neutral choice.<span class=\\\"redactor-invisible-space\\\"></span></p>\"},{\"id\":235,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":96,\"text\":\"<p>Today you will enjoy your very relaxed state of mind. It may take you a while getting there, but it's worth it.</p>\"},{\"id\":6,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":42,\"dislikes\":6,\"order\":99,\"text\":\"<p>Today is a crucial day for your emotional biorhythm. You can expect mood swings from one extreme to another. Fear and panic attacks are expected, as well as irritability, sensitivity, and lack of self-confidence.</p>\"},{\"id\":10,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":9,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":99,\"text\":\"<p>Your energy is weakening, and even ordinary things require much more energy than usual. Do not overload yourself with work, as any activity will require a higher concentration. It's time to relax and recover. Support your body with healthy food and vitamins.</p>\"},{\"id\":98,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":17,\"dislikes\":1,\"order\":99,\"text\":\"<p>In the critical phase of the intelligent biorhythm, the risk of errors increases. Do not make important decisions at this time: the consequences can be the most undesirable.</p>\"},{\"id\":145,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":102,\"text\":\"<p>Preserve the energy you've got and try to recharge your batteries by being nice to yourself. Don't blame yourself for not shooting for the stars at the moment, instead treat yourself with a trip to the country or a cosy evening with a favorite movie and a cup of tea.</p>\"},{\"id\":189,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":102,\"text\":\"<p>Some people might let you down today. A sense of aggression will arise in you, with which you will deal gently to defeat the circumstance.</p>\"},{\"id\":234,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4253,\"dislikes\":216,\"order\":102,\"text\":\"<p>Your eagerness to become a well-known person is forthwith going to be succeeded, if you do not experience any barriers in-between. Continue performing your best, regardless of the hurdles.</p>\"},{\"id\":144,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":105,\"text\":\"<p>Be attentive to what your body asks for. If it's a gentle stretching or yoga practice, do it. If it's staying in bed a little longer in the morning, do it too.</p>\"},{\"id\":188,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2035,\"dislikes\":81,\"order\":105,\"text\":\"<p>Plan something to do with a group of your friends. Suggest a long walk or hike in beautiful surroundings. Past has gone, don't even think about it.</p>\"},{\"id\":233,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":105,\"text\":\"<p>You might feel emotionally vulnerable these days, but this won't stay like it for long. Just find the things that bring you strength and confidence.</p>\"},{\"id\":143,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3816,\"dislikes\":137,\"order\":108,\"text\":\"<p>The lack of energy is absolutely normal for you right now and can be easily managed with some self-care, healthy diet and good rest.</p>\"},{\"id\":187,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":108,\"text\":\"<p>Originality in you is helping you move ahead in life as you are becoming successful, but it can be possible that some hurdles come your way.</p>\"},{\"id\":232,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":108,\"text\":\"<p>Personality is the most magnificent thing which you possess, which gives you insight into life. Don't doubt yourself.</p>\"},{\"id\":52,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":28,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":111,\"text\":\"<p>You begin to experience a deficit of energy: current affairs require strength, a feeling of laziness appears: it is your body that signals the approach of a critical phase of the physical biorhythm. At this time, you should not overload yourself with additional tasks.</p>\"},{\"id\":68,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":111,\"text\":\"<p>Any failure in creativity breaks your heart, and you meet even minimal criticism with hostility, gushing negative emotions. Touchiness can provoke conflicts and even the breakdown of social ties.</p>\"},{\"id\":97,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":22,\"dislikes\":6,\"order\":111,\"text\":\"<p>During this period, it is not only difficult for you to learn new things, but also to perform well-established and straightforward business operations. Even routine tasks are time-consuming. At this time, you should not go to interviews or present your ideas – it will be difficult for you to logically substantiate and defend them.</p>\"},{\"id\":142,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":114,\"text\":\"<p>You might feel a little worn out these days if you don't keep you work-life balance. Make sure you have time for good sleep and rest.</p>\"},{\"id\":186,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1709,\"dislikes\":64,\"order\":114,\"text\":\"<p>Abundance of care will swing your mood today from bad to good, and you will feel better than before. On the other hand, sudden changes in your lifestyle might make you feel a bit shaky.</p>\"},{\"id\":231,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":114,\"text\":\"<p>Consider showing gratitude towards others always in your mind. You might feel you are not in the state of giving right now, but you are more than you think.</p>\"},{\"id\":141,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":117,\"text\":\"<p>Be gentle to yourself and try not to push yourself to the limits. It's the time to gain and preserve energy but not waste it.</p>\"},{\"id\":185,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":117,\"text\":\"<p>Today is a neutral day for you, where you will undergo many difficult challenges as well as the energy to handle them. Dash ahead, and there is a chance to win or to lose, which depends on yours ability to handle them.</p>\"},{\"id\":230,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":117,\"text\":\"<p>Don't let your abrogating thoughts about your love life demolish your life. Focus on positive things, because there's always a silver lining.</p>\"},{\"id\":51,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":28,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":120,\"text\":\"<p>Metabolism in your body gradually slows down: activity decreases, reaction and endurance indicators deteriorate. You are still coping with the usual loads, but rush at work can unsettle you during this period.</p>\"},{\"id\":67,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":36,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":120,\"text\":\"<p>It becomes more difficult for you to communicate with others: it seems that you are not understood. Sensitivity and irritability increase. In the field of creativity, it is challenging to create something new without self-repetition</p>\"},{\"id\":96,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":47,\"dislikes\":2,\"order\":120,\"text\":\"<p>Mental activity begins to decline: it's time for your brain to rest. At this time, it is better to solve routine tasks that do not require mental strain. It is not worth reading \\\"difficult\\\" literature during this period.</p>\"},{\"id\":140,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2954,\"dislikes\":72,\"order\":123,\"text\":\"<p>Keep your mind on what brings you joy, fulfillment and strengths. There's no need to push yourself to the limits now, listen to your body and give it what it asks for.</p>\"},{\"id\":184,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1954,\"dislikes\":37,\"order\":123,\"text\":\"You need to be conscious all the time about keeping your mind focused on what matters the most for you right now. Though, you will get some joyous moments with your family or friends too.\"},{\"id\":229,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":5214,\"dislikes\":100,\"order\":123,\"text\":\"<p>Listen to yourself closely. You are very intuitive right now.</p>\"},{\"id\":139,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":126,\"text\":\"<p>You should pay close attention both to workout and relaxation, otherwise you'll run out of energy quickly. Yoga practice or swimming are the best choices for you right now.</p>\"},{\"id\":183,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":126,\"text\":\"<p>You need to be conscious all the time about keeping your mind focused on what matters the most for you right now. Though, you will get some joyous moments with your family or friends too.</p>\"},{\"id\":228,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":126,\"text\":\"<p>It's a good idea to stay in and have a 'you' day. Treat yourself with your favorite music, movies and do something, that inspires you.</p>\"},{\"id\":50,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":25,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":129,\"text\":\"<p>You are still on the rise, but the body is beginning to conserve energy. You have enough strength for all the planned things, but you are already starting to feel a little tired. At this phase of the physical biorhythm, it is no longer worth setting super goals.</p>\"},{\"id\":66,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":1,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":129,\"text\":\"<p>Your social activity decreases, others begin to annoy. This is not the best period for first dates, establishing new friendships, or meeting the parents of a loved one.</p>\"},{\"id\":95,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":19,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":129,\"text\":\"<p>The \\\"tail\\\" of the intellectual ascent phase is the time to complete the complex intellectual work that you did in the previous stages. You still enjoy intellectual leisure, but you are already slightly \\\"slowing down\\\".</p>\"},{\"id\":138,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":1,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":132,\"text\":\"<p>You can go for more ambitious goals considering physical exercise like running, weightlifting or hiking. Just don't forget about resting afterwards.</p>\"},{\"id\":182,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2202,\"dislikes\":155,\"order\":132,\"text\":\"<p>Embrace yourself! Today is something going to happen, which has not happened to you yet regarding your love life. Soon you are going to be the choice of someone, but you have to be alert likewise. Someone may come between your way.</p>\"},{\"id\":227,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":132,\"text\":\"<p>Don't push yourself into anything you think you should do, but you don't want to. Instead focus on whatever brings you joy and satisfaction.</p>\"},{\"id\":137,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":3529,\"dislikes\":72,\"order\":135,\"text\":\"<p>Your endurance is building up these days. Pay attention to your diet and sleep and you'll be able to fight any challenges you want.</p>\"},{\"id\":181,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":135,\"text\":\"<p>Act smartly at the time of the interview as you are going to crack it with your smartness. The presence of high energy in you will benefit you with the purposes you want to fulfill in your life.</p>\"},{\"id\":226,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":135,\"text\":\"<p>You may be not that active and cheerful today, but this is a good day for self-care and reflection.</p>\"},{\"id\":136,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":138,\"text\":\"<p>This is a good phase for trying something new, like new sports or activities you wanted but never dare to do before.</p>\"},{\"id\":180,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":138,\"text\":\"<p>Today, the goals you have set can be achieved according to your comfort zone, which will suit you well, and you will be having a positive approach towards your profession.</p>\"},{\"id\":225,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":138,\"text\":\"<p>Even if you feel a little less stable right now, remember, this is not entirely true. You just need some rest and you'll feel reborn right after.</p>\"},{\"id\":23,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1986,\"dislikes\":54,\"order\":141,\"text\":\"<p>You’ll be going through a positive phase of the intellectual biorhythm. Logic, intellect, learning abilities, and concentration will be on top. You will handle any tasks quickly and effortlessly. Use this time to start new projects and get things in order.</p>\"},{\"id\":49,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":141,\"text\":\"<p>Exercise and lack of sleep in the phase of physical recovery do not have a negative effect. Even after the party you will feel like a cucumber in the morning. It takes less time to get a good rest.</p>\"},{\"id\":65,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":141,\"text\":\"<p>Your emotions are still in the \\\"unloading\\\" phase – you are ready to give warmth, be creative and actively communicate. But the approach of the next cycle is already felt – \\\"reboot\\\". Don't expect too much out of communication if your emotional cycle has entered this phase. Creativity is declining.</p>\"},{\"id\":135,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":1,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":144,\"text\":\"<p>Whatever you decide to do, keep your activities balanced and entertaining. Now is a favorable time for outdoor exercising or team sports.</p>\"},{\"id\":179,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":144,\"text\":\"<p>You are kind, gentle, and loving towards the people the whole day long, which is going to charge you with tons of compliments and praise. Hassle-free life has come to your doorstep.</p>\"},{\"id\":224,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4839,\"dislikes\":76,\"order\":144,\"text\":\"<p>Keep your mind clear and your heart open. You are still strong enough to overcome something that usually upsets you with ease.</p>\"},{\"id\":134,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2332,\"dislikes\":82,\"order\":147,\"text\":\"That's a wonderful time for pushing yourself a bit more in order to get the results you wish for. Your energy, confidence and will power is just right for challenging tasks.\"},{\"id\":178,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":147,\"text\":\"<p>Your energy is much sturdier than it has been over the past few days, and you can count on having a faithful attitude about things all day long. It is great news for you.</p>\"},{\"id\":223,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":147,\"text\":\"<p>The existence of warmth will take your life to the next level as your warming gesture will help others in the time of complications and they will adore you for that.</p>\"},{\"id\":9,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":38,\"dislikes\":1,\"order\":150,\"text\":\"<p>In the positive phase of the cycle, you can easily cope with increased stress, lack of sleep, and rest. Endurance, strength, and speed of reaction will help to achieve high results, especially in sports. You will feel much more confident, dynamic, and enterprising person.</p>\"},{\"id\":64,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":30,\"dislikes\":6,\"order\":150,\"text\":\"<p>The phase of emotional uplift is characterized by an increase in social productivity: this is the time for sincere conversations, eliminating communication errors and restoring lost relationships.</p>\"},{\"id\":94,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1767,\"dislikes\":46,\"order\":150,\"text\":\"<p>During the period of mental recovery, you can cope with the work routine faster. Analytical work and brainstorming sessions will be productive during this phase.</p>\"},{\"id\":133,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":153,\"text\":\"<p>This is a favorable time for taking risks and testing your strengths and endurance since you are in good shape physically and mentally. Use your time wisely and with pleasure.</p>\"},{\"id\":177,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":153,\"text\":\"<p>Unleash all of your emotions and let the whole world know what you are feeling deep in your heart as this is the best opportunity to disclose your feelings because you have no fear of the audience.</p>\"},{\"id\":222,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":153,\"text\":\"<p>It's a good idea to improve inner peace while communicating with some of your close friends.</p>\"},{\"id\":176,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":156,\"text\":\"You are going to have a thrilling weekend with lots of sudden surprises and joyful events around. Enjoy them to the fullest. You are in a phase of life when your expectations are high, and they are getting accomplished too.\"},{\"id\":221,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":156,\"text\":\"<p>It's the great time now to open yourself to your close people a bit more, since you feel confident and happy with yourself.</p>\"},{\"id\":5,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2026,\"dislikes\":44,\"order\":159,\"text\":\"<p>Today you’re absorbing knowledge like a sponge. Information will be processing really easily, so don’t hesitate and take on any kinds of study. Any mental activity at this time will bring visible results. Don’t be afraid to make plans, start on new things, and generate ideas.</p>\"},{\"id\":48,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":18,\"dislikes\":1,\"order\":159,\"text\":\"<p>The positive phase of the biorhythm is characterized by a slight excess of physical strength and excellent health. Your immunity during this period is especially reliable, and your body requires stress. If you have nowhere to direct your energy, you can just turn on your favorite music and dance.</p>\"},{\"id\":132,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2422,\"dislikes\":179,\"order\":159,\"text\":\"<p>It's a positive phase of your health and physical state, enjoy it! There is nothing you can't do now, so feel free to run a marathon, go mountain skiing or even skydiving. If extreme sports is not your thing, just do whatever feels right, even if it's just a walk at the beach</p>\"},{\"id\":220,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":159,\"text\":\"<p>Good mental and emotional health is assured if you keep yourself occupied with some work and enjoy working as much as you can.</p>\"},{\"id\":7,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":3868,\"dislikes\":242,\"order\":162,\"text\":\"<p>You’re feeling inspiration and enthusiasm, a burst of energy, and a great mood. It’s easy to begin on new things and make new acquaintances in this emotional state. Any negotiations, discussions or dates will lead to the desired results.</p>\"},{\"id\":131,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":162,\"text\":\"<p>Finding joy in whatever you do is easy for you now since your body experiences an energy boost in this phase. It's a good time to try something exciting and new, because your strong health and great vitality will help you overcome any complications you may face.\\r\\n</p>\"},{\"id\":175,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":162,\"text\":\"<p>You have got solid self-integrity, which will help you step right up and start talking. Others are bound to be impressed by your confidence and charm. Don't freeze in your approach. Just keep going ahead.</p>\"},{\"id\":130,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":165,\"text\":\"<p>You are in a good place right now considering your physical condition, health and energy. You don't have to take any extra efforts to achieve any results you want, you'll get there with ease. Enjoy it!</p>\"},{\"id\":174,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1853,\"dislikes\":46,\"order\":165,\"text\":\"<p>Whether you are looking for a new friend, a new business connection, or new love, the possibilities abound! Initiate a conversation with someone you have always been a little bit diffident around.</p>\"},{\"id\":219,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":165,\"text\":\"<p>You get success in most of your life events because of the presence of good humor in you, which is shown when you are emotionally strong.</p>\"},{\"id\":129,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2370,\"dislikes\":167,\"order\":168,\"text\":\"Take your time to explore your abilities since you are in a great physical shape now for experimenting. Try a new kind of sports or raise your bar a little higher in the activity you normally do. Any of this will bring you great result and satisfaction.\"},{\"id\":173,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":168,\"text\":\"<p>If you are feeling outgoing right now, this can be a day for you to shine truly! It is time to get those names and numbers that can make your life more rewarding and cheerful.</p>\"},{\"id\":218,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":168,\"text\":\"<p>Don't be surprised that nowadays you attract so many people, especially since now you are so emotionally well-balanced.</p>\"},{\"id\":4,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":27,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":171,\"text\":\"<p>Now, you are in a positive biorhythm phase. Your physical activity is on height, and immunity is invincible. A surge of energy and vitality will ensure success in any matter. Take a walk in the park or go in for sports - today it will bring you great pleasure!</p>\"},{\"id\":63,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":28,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":171,\"text\":\"<p>Some expressiveness characterizes the positive phase of the emotional biorhythm – even reserved people become more open and frank. The establishment of new social ties is possible.</p>\"},{\"id\":93,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1638,\"dislikes\":42,\"order\":171,\"text\":\"<p>Intelligent lifting is the optimal period for performing work that requires intellectual exertion: during this time, such tasks will be especially easy. If you have an interview, this is the best moment: you will be able to show off your mental abilities</p>\"},{\"id\":128,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":174,\"text\":\"<p>You feel like your physical abilities are unlimited and it is quite true at the moment. This is a perfect time to dedicate yourself to doing sports or being physically active in any kind since you'll feel the emotional uplift and fulfillment too.</p>\"},{\"id\":172,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":174,\"text\":\"<p>You are filled with positive energy today, and whatever you will do today is going to be the hit. All you need to do is to be calm and peaceful. Your presence is in high demand.</p>\"},{\"id\":217,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":174,\"text\":\"<p>Your mental health is stable today, which enables you to perform well in your tasks, and you will get an appreciation for that too.</p>\"},{\"id\":127,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":177,\"text\":\"<p>Your strengths, concentration, reaction and speed are at their peak. Any activities which require such qualities are highly recommended. You can get wonderful result playing team sports as well as practicing on your own.</p>\"},{\"id\":171,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":177,\"text\":\"<p><strong></strong>You are full of power today, which will enable you to perform well in your ongoing tasks and will give you a huge success in that. Keep up the good work.</p>\"},{\"id\":216,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4244,\"dislikes\":94,\"order\":177,\"text\":\"<p>Your sensitivity can give you an advantage in creating a positive contact with your inner self and with others. It doesn't make you weak, on the opposite, it makes you great.</p>\"},{\"id\":2,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":38,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":180,\"text\":\"<p>In a time of emotional uplift, you feel like taking action, being creative, and generating new ideas. Use the inspiration and delight to start on new projects, socialize, meet your friends or your significant other. Don’t miss those moments!</p>\"},{\"id\":3,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1956,\"dislikes\":63,\"order\":180,\"text\":\"<p>Today you can easily absorb new information and will have no problem concentrating on challenging tasks. It’s an excellent time for studies, intellectual challenges, and online-courses. You will solve any issues most efficiently.</p>\"},{\"id\":47,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2492,\"dislikes\":106,\"order\":180,\"text\":\"<p>Physical activity is at its maximum. Tempering, exercising in the gym and even walking in the fresh air will bring positive results. During this period, you will cope with any tasks – from general cleaning to kayaking.</p>\"},{\"id\":126,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":183,\"text\":\"<p>You are in a great shape now, so don't waste your time sitting on a couch doubting yourself. Go out for a run or stay in and do some indoor training. It will bring you more satisfaction than you expect.</p>\"},{\"id\":170,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1945,\"dislikes\":47,\"order\":183,\"text\":\"<p>Today you are highly encouraged with what you are doing in life towards others and keep doing so. It can give you a higher chance of unconditional enlightenment.</p>\"},{\"id\":215,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":183,\"text\":\"<p>Since you are emotionally strong, it gives you the strength to fight in all the circumstances. So if life gives you a challenge, don't worry, you'll deal with it.</p>\"},{\"id\":125,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":186,\"text\":\"<p>You can do whatever you want now and be good at it. Sports, swimming, jogging or even cleaning the house - all of it will bring you joy and fun.</p>\"},{\"id\":169,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":186,\"text\":\"<p>Maintain your standards as the way they are. Nobody is going to harm you since your energy level is too high at the moment. With your abilities, you will rise and shine.</p>\"},{\"id\":214,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2536,\"dislikes\":76,\"order\":186,\"text\":\"<p>You have the ability to adjust yourself to the demands and heartfelt responses of others. You possess certain strengths today.</p>\"},{\"id\":1,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":74,\"dislikes\":12,\"order\":189,\"text\":\"<p>Your activity is at maximum. Any action doesn't require much energy. You can achieve excellent results. Exercises in the open air can give you more energy and a sharper mind.</p>\"},{\"id\":62,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":33,\"dislikes\":3,\"order\":189,\"text\":\"<p>Emotional biorhythm is in the maximum phase. Communicate more – social communication will be pleasant and rewarding. Take time for creative self-realization – during this period you have every chance to create a small masterpiece.</p>\"},{\"id\":92,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":1811,\"dislikes\":43,\"order\":189,\"text\":\"<p>During this period, you have intellectual needs that require satisfaction. Read special or popular science literature, play board games.</p>\"},{\"id\":124,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2269,\"dislikes\":128,\"order\":192,\"text\":\"<p>Have a great time experiencing the peak of your energy. Do any physical activities you like since you've got to find the way out for it.</p>\"},{\"id\":168,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":192,\"text\":\"<p>Moving forward, you can resolve your problems very quickly. Any hurdles in your way will be disappearing with the controlling method you will use, and your journey will be filled with happiness.</p>\"},{\"id\":213,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":4774,\"dislikes\":176,\"order\":192,\"text\":\"<p>Strong affection towards someone will charge you up, and your day will be loaded with pleasure.</p>\"},{\"id\":123,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":195,\"text\":\"<p>This is your positive biorhythm phase and you should dare yourself do something you might doubt before. Don't worry, you'll get great result and pleasure in trying something new in sports or daily physical activities.</p>\"},{\"id\":167,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2176,\"dislikes\":52,\"order\":195,\"text\":\"<p>If you are going to begin with your studies soon, it would be the right time for that too. Boost yourself and get ready because the time has come where you will be able to overcome the current challenges.</p>\"},{\"id\":212,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":195,\"text\":\"<p>Your biorhythm has the positive spark. Your emotions will be in control today, and you are emotionally intelligent. It will bring satisfaction and stability in your love life.</p>\"},{\"id\":122,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":2390,\"dislikes\":163,\"order\":198,\"text\":\"Your physical strengths  is at its best now, so if you wanted to set a personal record, now it's a perfect time! Enjoy every moment of it and set yourself ambitious goals.\"},{\"id\":166,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":2124,\"dislikes\":40,\"order\":198,\"text\":\"<p>You have easy access to gather the bulk of new information through which you are in a state to express yourself to the fullest in front of others, and you have become so confident that you hardly have any fear of standing alone too.</p>\"},{\"id\":211,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":0,\"dislikes\":0,\"order\":198,\"text\":\"<p>Your mood is going to flourish today due to the uplift you feel. You'll do great whatever you decide to do today!</p>\"},{\"id\":46,\"category\":\"physical\",\"likes\":4475,\"dislikes\":306,\"order\":200,\"text\":\"Vitality reaches its peak: energy is in full swing, and you need to give it the right outlet. At this time, it is worth focusing on sports, work in the country, and go on a hike. If you are thinking of setting a personal best, this is the perfect time!\"},{\"id\":61,\"category\":\"emotional\",\"likes\":6673,\"dislikes\":664,\"order\":200,\"text\":\"<p>You are at the peak of positive: positive emotions are overwhelming, you are socially active, you are happy to communicate with friends and family, you are engaged in creativity. This is a productive period, including for romantic relationships.</p>\"},{\"id\":91,\"category\":\"intellectual\",\"likes\":5839,\"dislikes\":145,\"order\":200,\"text\":\"<p>The peak of the intellectual biorhythm is the maximum of your thinking abilities. During this period, you are able to quickly and correctly solve complex intellectual problems, and your logic and erudition work flawlessly. During this period, you turn into a \\\"family detective\\\", and at work amaze your superiors with your sharp mind.</p>\"}]"
          },
