          "content": {
            "size": 10109,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":4,\"planet\":\"mercury\",\"tags\":[\"Tech glitches\",\"Miscommunication\",\"Forgetfulness\"],\"description\":\"<p>Mercury rules communication, thinking, learning, travel, and technology. During Mercury retrograde, it's best to review past plans rather than start major new projects. Be patient and double-check all details to avoid miscommunications and delays.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Misunderstandings and arguments\",\"Delays in travel or shipping\",\"Emails or messages getting lost\",\"Tech glitches or data errors\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":16,\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"do\":\"Use this period to revisit creative projects, reconnect with old friends, and dive deep into spiritual practices or journaling.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid signing contracts, overcommitting emotionally, or relying solely on intuition for major decisions.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I reconnect with my intuition?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_16_689c70cdab8f1.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"pisces\"]},{\"id\":19,\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"do\":\"Take time to nurture family connections, revisit memories, and create emotional security through thoughtful reflection and home organization.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid taking things too personally, initiating serious relationship talks, or making big decisions based on nostalgia.\\r\\n\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I better nurture my emotional needs?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_19_689c710a0aa10.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"cancer\"]},{\"id\":22,\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"do\":\"Reflect on past emotional patterns, reassess financial agreements, and focus on inner healing.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid digging up old grudges, making impulsive investments, or engaging in power struggles.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Where in my life do I need to let go of control?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_22_689c718e95e5e.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"scorpio\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"sign\":\"pisces\"},{\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"sign\":\"cancer\"},{\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\"}]},{\"id\":7,\"planet\":\"venus\",\"tags\":[\"Love tension\",\"Financial confusion\",\"Style regrets\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Venus retrograde, past lovers or unresolved emotions may resurface, and it's not the ideal time for cosmetic changes or big financial decisions. Reflect on what (and who) you truly value.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Old loves reappearing\",\"Misunderstandings in relationships\",\"Second-guessing style choices\",\"Unexpected expenses\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":25,\"start\":\"2026-10-03\",\"end\":\"2026-11-14\",\"do\":\"Reconnect with past relationships or creative projects and gather inspiration for new creative projects.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid drastic makeovers, luxury purchases, or cosmetic procedures, or don’t start new romantic relationships.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do my relationships reflect who I really am?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_25_689c7176c39f4.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"libra\",\"scorpio\"]}],\"signs\":[]},{\"id\":10,\"planet\":\"mars\",\"tags\":[\"Low motivation\",\"Frustration\",\"Flashbacks\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Mars retrograde, anger simmers, old conflicts may resurface, and direct action often backfires. Rather than pushing forward, reflect on your goals and how you channel your energy.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Burnout or loss of motivation\",\"Arguments resurfacing\",\"Delays in physical goals\",\"Passive-aggressive behavior\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":34,\"start\":\"2027-01-10\",\"end\":\"2027-04-01\",\"do\":\"Finish an old project, create a painting, write a poem, and recall what you used to love.\",\"dont\":\"Do intense workouts, make impulsive decisions, or engage in heated arguments.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do my daily actions reflect the passion I want to live with?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_34_689c71ba2e78f.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"leo\",\"virgo\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2027-01-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-21\",\"sign\":\"virgo\"},{\"start\":\"2027-02-21\",\"end\":\"2027-04-01\",\"sign\":\"leo\"}]},{\"id\":13,\"planet\":\"jupiter\",\"tags\":[\"Inner reflection\",\"Delays in progress\",\"Rewriting your truth\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Jupiter retrograde, this is a time to reassess your personal philosophy, goals for growth, and what you truly consider meaningful. Instead of chasing more, focus on refining what you already have.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Doubts about long-term plans\",\"Revisit of moral beliefs\",\"Delays in travel or education\",\"Second-guessing decisions\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":37,\"start\":\"2025-11-11\",\"end\":\"2026-03-11\",\"do\":\"Revisit your roots, explore ancestral healing, and create a safe, nourishing space for emotional renewal and self-care.\",\"dont\":\"Ignore gut feelings, rush through emotional growth, or make major real estate or family-related decisions without reflection.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Have I built a life that truly feels like home — within and around me?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_37_689c70b0d01b2.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"cancer\"]},{\"id\":40,\"start\":\"2026-12-13\",\"end\":\"2027-04-13\",\"do\":\"Spend time refining your creative voice, reconnect with inner confidence, and reflect on how you express love, leadership, and joy.\",\"dont\":\"Overdramatize situations, chase attention for the wrong reasons, or make risky decisions in love or career for the sake of image.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"What would it look like to make decisions with heart, not ego?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_40_689c71a3e8ea3.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"leo\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2025-11-11\",\"end\":\"2026-03-11\",\"sign\":\"cancer\"},{\"start\":\"2026-12-13\",\"end\":\"2027-04-13\",\"sign\":\"leo\"}]},{\"id\":16,\"planet\":\"saturn\",\"tags\":[\"Boundaries tested\",\"Discipline redefined\",\"Long-term vision reset\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Saturn retrograde, life's lessons return for revision. Reexamine commitments, boundaries, and long-term responsibilities. Saturn retrograde offers a chance to rewrite the rules you live by.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Revisit past responsibilities\",\"Question career paths\",\"Tests of patience and discipline\",\"Push to define your boundaries\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":46,\"start\":\"2026-07-26\",\"end\":\"2026-12-10\",\"do\":\"Finish long-delayed personal goals, practice patience with new projects, and exercise regularly.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid accountability, force things that aren’t ready, or make quick choices just to feel in control.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Am I building something meaningful right now?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_46_689c7141e9b29.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aries\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-07-26\",\"end\":\"2026-12-10\",\"sign\":\"aries\"}]},{\"id\":19,\"planet\":\"uranus\",\"tags\":[\"Hurried awakening\",\"Inner rebellion\",\"Sudden insights\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Uranus retrograde, the planet of disruption turns inward, triggering inner revolutions, surprise realizations, and a need to break free from outdated systems. Rather than chasing external change, examine where you're resisting necessary transformation within.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Restless or restricted feeling\",\"Desire to break routines\",\"Old patterns resurfacing\",\"Technological or ideological glitches\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":58,\"start\":\"2026-09-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-08\",\"do\":\"Journal, reconnect with forgotten studies and explore new ways to express your truth.\",\"dont\":\"Rush into new contracts, overthink, or neglect your mental health.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Are my thoughts and words truly my own?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_58_689c715c010a7.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"gemini\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-09-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-08\",\"sign\":\"gemini\"}]},{\"id\":22,\"planet\":\"neptune\",\"tags\":[\"Clouded clarity\",\"Daily illusions\",\"Heightened intuition\"],\"description\":\"<p>When Neptune goes retrograde, disillusionment occurs, fantasies unravel, and truths hidden beneath dreams come to light. It's a time to confront escapism, substance habits, or spiritual bypassing and realign with deeper, more authentic visions.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Realizations about self-delusion\",\"Old dreams reevaluation\",\"Heightened spiritual sensitivity\",\"Feeling ungrounded\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":67,\"start\":\"2026-07-07\",\"end\":\"2026-12-12\",\"do\":\"Spend time alone in nature, reflect on past leadership roles, and work on solo creative projects.\",\"dont\":\"Use independence as an excuse, rush into new roles or identities, or react impulsively.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How flexible is my mind when facing uncertainty?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_67_689c712b5ead5.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aries\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-07-07\",\"end\":\"2026-12-12\",\"sign\":\"aries\"}]},{\"id\":25,\"planet\":\"pluto\",\"tags\":[\"Deep excavation\",\"Power reversals\",\"Shadow confrontations\"],\"description\":\"<p>When Pluto, the planet of transformation and the underworld, turns retrograde, it invites you to dive beneath the surface and face what’s been buried. Shed toxic attachments, confront control issues, and reclaim personal power. Instead of fearing the dark, explore it.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Intensified inner work\",\"Old wounds resurfacing\",\"Shifts in power dynamics\",\"Release of what no longer serves\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":73,\"start\":\"2026-05-06\",\"end\":\"2026-10-16\",\"do\":\"Delete outdated accounts, review who has access to your data, or explore therapy, coaching, or inner work focused on trust issues.\",\"dont\":\"Ghost your friends, quit a community impulsively, or ignore burnout or mental fatigue.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do I trust my inner compass?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_73_689c70efb09ff.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aquarius\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-05-06\",\"end\":\"2026-10-16\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\"}]}]"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:48:37.797Z"
      },
      {
        "_connectionId": "6013",
        "cache": {},
