          ],
          "queryString": [],
          "bodySize": 0
        },
        "response": {
          "status": 200,
          "statusText": "",
          "httpVersion": "http/2.0",
          "headers": [
            {
              "name": "content-type",
              "value": "application/json; charset=UTF-8"
            }
          ],
          "content": {
            "size": 71287,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"house_number\":1,\"title\":\"1st house\",\"influence\":\"awareness of self\",\"planet\":\"Mars \",\"meaning\":\"personality, appearance, position about life, self-esteem\",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, lower  \",\"description\":\"The 1st house is the location of your ascendant or rising sign, which speaks to how you present yourself out in the world. It shows how you express yourself and how others see you, determining your behavior and character traits. \\r\\nThis house also speaks to your manners and physical appearance, so look at the zodiac sign that rules this house to see how you make a first impression.\",\"zone\":\"the first 1/3 of the circle  \",\"type\":\"corner  \",\"axis\":\"1/7  \",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Ascendant in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"ascendant\",\"description\":\"Your ascendant or rising sign always rules your first house of self. This means it holds the key to understanding your outer appearance, self-identity, and overall self-expression.\\r\\n\\r\\nThink of it as the mask you wear, the first impression you make on others. It's also the filter through which you experience the world, shaping your unique personality and outlook.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Sun in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You are all about making a grand entrance and being noticed. You take pride in your appearance and project a strong image. However, you are also very self-conscious and rely a lot on the opinions of those around you.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust remember to focus on being authentically you rather than obsessing over what others think. As a natural-born leader and innovator, embrace the role yet be careful not to be too bossy.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"Your feelings and emotional reactions are very obvious to those around you. You may come across as sensitive, impulsive, or nurturing, depending on the situation. You need to express yourself freely and constantly explore to feel fulfilled.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour mood tends to change frequently, and you may take things too personally or react too quickly. Learning to understand others' emotions and not always putting your own first will be important for growth.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a clever, playful, and curious personality. You are quick to adapt to new situations, especially intellectually. You have a tendency toward logical thinking rather than empathy. You also have a restless nature and may have a hard time staying focused.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour appearance and mannerisms could change pretty often. You enjoy talking but may monopolize conversations or not listen well because you are already thinking of your next response.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You have a friendly, magnetic, and attractive personality that draws people to you effortlessly. You are diplomatic, warm, and charming in all your interactions. Your natural sense of style and presence is captivating to others.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, be aware of negative tendencies like being superficial or playing dumb to avoid conflict. Don't let the need to be liked by others overshadow your power and confidence.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"You are not one to conform to societal norms and expectations. You embrace your individuality and have a unique sense of style and self-expression. You are bold and confident in letting your authentic self shine. Your ultimate goal is to make a positive impact on the world.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour loved ones may find you unpredictable at times, but they know that your intentions are always well-meaning and genuine. You may have bursts of intense passion, but you also have a tendency to lose interest quickly.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"As a dynamic and enterprising individual, you jump into new situations with energy and enthusiasm but may struggle with follow-through. Some may see you as aggressive or rash, but others are impressed by your fiery spirit.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a strong need for independence and action, and competition motivates you. Spontaneity is key for you, and you may stir up trouble when bored. Your approach to life is physical and active, and you enjoy taking the lead.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You have a positive and optimistic presence, always starting new endeavors with faith and enthusiasm. Your strong moral compass guides you in making decisions. Others may see you as lucky, but your resourcefulness and strong sense of self-worth are what truly lead to success.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou value comfort and material possessions, finding joy in the physical world. Be careful not to overindulge in them. Your natural charm and ability to connect with others will bring success to your ventures.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You may have a serious and reserved demeanor, but when you smile, your stern image fades. Saturn in the first house can make you more aware of societal expectations and responsibilities, causing you to put others' needs before your own.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis can lead to feelings of guilt and anxiety, causing you to become overly attached to your surroundings. Remember to prioritize yourself and communicate your needs with others. Finding a partner who understands your desire for self-assertion will bring balance to your life.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You may present yourself as artistic, gentle, and dreamy, especially if Neptune is close to your Ascendant. You are highly sensitive to your environment and others' perceptions of you. People may see you differently depending on their own views and feelings.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a calming and alluring presence that draws others to you. Your imagination is powerful, but you may struggle with a strong sense of identity and being easily influenced by others. You have a go-with-the-flow attitude and a peaceful nature.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 1\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have a powerful presence and often leave a lasting impression on others. Your strong and intense energy can be intimidating, whether intentional or not. You value your privacy and have a mysterious aura that intrigues others.\\r\\n\\r\\nFear of being controlled, rejected, or overlooked may lead you to always appear confident and determined. You tend to see beyond the surface and always look for hidden meaning. Learning to pick your battles and not always seeing life as a battleground will be important.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":2,\"title\":\"2nd house\",\"influence\":\"possessions \",\"planet\":\"Venus \",\"meaning\":\"finance, talents, personal resources, property  \",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, lower        \",\"description\":\"The 2nd house determines your attitude toward wealth and your capacity for saving or spending money. In a broad sense, it is responsible for everything that you possess, especially the benefits you receive for your work. \\r\\nConsider the zodiac sign that rules this house in your chart to understand how you approach money and set financial goals.\",\"zone\":\" the first 1/3 of the circle  \",\"type\":\"follow  \",\"axis\":\"2/8 \",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"For you, stability and material success are key. You take pride in what you own and have a strong drive for security. Being known for your strong sense of responsibility, you are not the one to let others down once you’ve made a promise.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust be careful not to define yourself solely by material possessions. Instead, focus on your values and your ability to commit and follow through. Your lasting relationships and consistent routines speak for themselves.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"Money can trigger both your generous and frivolous nature, as well as your frugal and anxious side. You have a fear of debt and a strong need for financial stability. Saving money is a priority for you.\\r\\n\\r\\nOccasionally, you may indulge in impulsive shopping when feeling emotionally frustrated. You may also hold onto possessions and people, seeking admiration and validation from them. Over time, learn to value yourself and find your own sense of worth.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a very practical mind and find it easy to come up with solutions to problems that others may overlook. However, you prefer to work at your own pace and don't like being rushed. This applies to studying as well.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can be quite stubborn in your opinions and don't enjoy compromising. You have a strong connection to the physical world and value sensual experiences over abstract concepts.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You appreciate and seek out material possessions as a form of love and affection. Your taste is refined, and others may think of you as stylish and extravagant. You have a talent for finding valuable items and are attracted to quality.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may use your generosity to gain material rewards and can be easily swayed by admiration from a partner. But once committed, you are loyal and devoted. You hold strong values and beliefs that are not easily influenced by others.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"Your perspective on possessions and money is quite different from most. You see them as a means to an end, to support your desire for freedom and a nontraditional lifestyle. You may be content with very little material possessions as long as you can still have the freedom to live life on your own terms.\\r\\n\\r\\nAlternatively, you may value money if they can provide the financial resources for your unconventional desires. Your personal values may also be unconventional and align with your desire for independence and uniqueness.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You are a hard worker and enjoy producing things of practical value. However, you may be impulsive when it comes to spending money. You value independence and take pride in your possessions and achievements.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour physical abilities and stamina are important for your self-worth, as you may have a strong appetite for sensual and sexual experiences. Defending your values is important to you, and you are fiercely determined.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"People may envy your seemingly lucky financial and material circumstances, but in reality, you are resourceful and driven to achieve success. You appreciate the pleasures of comfort and luxury, but watch out for overindulging.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour strong self-worth and confidence contribute to your success in attracting wealth and abundance. Remember to stay grounded and humble as you enjoy your successes.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"Traditional astrology may see Saturn in this house as a barrier to wealth, but we see it as a personal attitude toward material possessions. You may have a pessimistic view of your ability to attain wealth or may be overly cautious with your finances.\\r\\n\\r\\nBeing too risk-averse can limit your financial growth, but remaining aware of this attitude can turn it into a strength. Instead of letting fear hold you back, carefully plan and strategize your investments to build long-term stability.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"Money and material possessions may not hold much value to you, and this could cause some money troubles if you neglect to give it the necessary attention. You have a generous spirit, but be careful not to get taken advantage of.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a deep intuitive sense when it comes to making money, but it's important to trust in your own self-worth rather than relying on luck or daydreams of sudden wealth. Seek practical financial advice for success.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 2\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have strong instincts when it comes to money and acquiring possessions. You may have a hard time letting go of things due to sentimental value or fear of not having enough. Some may struggle with a need for control over their finances and possessions.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may be protective of your belongings and prefer others to ask before taking them. You have a keen eye for spotting valuable things and are skilled at planning and strategizing to increase your wealth. Others may seek your advice on financial matters.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":3,\"title\":\"3rd house\",\"influence\":\"environment\",\"planet\":\"Mercury \",\"meaning\":\"wishes, efforts, relatives \",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, lower \",\"description\":\"The 3rd house focuses on communication and relationships. It reveals how open you are to new acquaintances, how comfortable you feel around others, and how you express your thoughts. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign that rules this house in your chart for hints on your communication style, the way you learn and teach, and how you get your message across to the world.\",\"zone\":\"the first 1/3 of the circle      \",\"type\":\"сadent \",\"axis\":\"3/9 \",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You are a smart, curious soul, always seeking new knowledge and experiences. You take pride in your mental agility and great ability to connect with others. You are able to adapt quite easily to whatever environment you are in.\\r\\n\\r\\nBut don't let your need for variety and stimulation lead to restlessness. Embrace your communication skills and share your knowledge without trying to always be the smartest person in the room.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You are highly responsive, curious, and communicative. You have a talent for picking up on moods and adapting to others' ways of thinking. As you grow, you will learn to balance your logical mind with your emotional depth. Your opinions and ideas change often, and you may struggle to assert your own thoughts.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are sensitive to others' opinions and may even adopt their ideas as your own. Learning to own your unique thoughts and feelings is crucial for growth.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a natural curiosity and enjoy reading, teaching, and exchanging ideas with others. However, you may have a hard time staying focused and can become easily distracted. You are a fast learner and love to share your knowledge with others through talking.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are also very involved in your community and may be quite chatty. You thrive on the latest news and gossip, but this can lead to nervousness or fidgeting at times.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You are a smooth talker who knows just what to say to win people over. Diplomatic and tactful, you have a way with words that others find charming and appealing. Compliments come effortlessly to you.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust be careful not to use flattery for your own benefit or engage in mind games with others. Your love for mental stimulation and variety in relationships may also make it challenging to find lasting love.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"In your interactions with peers and siblings, you always add a touch of eccentricity and humor. You have a creative and offbeat way of expressing yourself that often makes people smile.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may not always follow traditional ways of communicating or making connections, but your creativity and individuality set you apart in the best way possible. While some people may find you puzzling or annoying, most appreciate your open-mindedness and sincerity.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"When it comes to speaking your mind, you never hold back. Some may find you too direct, but you know a lot about a wide range of topics and love sharing your knowledge with others. You have a talent for debate and can easily get fired up about even the smallest matters.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour communication style can be provocative, even if that's not your intention. At your best, you inspire others with your enthusiasm and lively expression. You are also fiercely protective of your opinions, beliefs, and loved ones.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You are a natural communicator, always curious and seeking new knowledge and connections with others. People turn to you for advice because of your ability to see the big picture.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour genuine interest in others makes you a social butterfly, putting others at ease in your presence. Your optimistic and forward-thinking mindset will help you excel in areas such as teaching, writing, or public speaking.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You tend to be reserved and uncomfortable in familiar surroundings and interactions with others. This may make you appear distant or cold, but you can use this to your advantage by listening more and speaking less.\\r\\n\\r\\nSaturn's influence in this house may also lead to feelings of self-doubt and anxiety in daily life. Focus on self-acceptance and let go of unnecessary guilt. A supportive partner can help you feel more at ease and confident in your communication.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"Traditional learning may not be your strong suit, as you have a more artistic and visual way of understanding information. Sticking to schedules and keeping up with daily tasks can be challenging, as you are often lost in your imagination.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a natural charm and understanding of others, making your communication style creative and easygoing. However, be careful not to be too vague in your language, as this could lead to misunderstandings.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 3\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"Your mind is analytical, and you have a thirst for knowledge beyond the surface. You can be persuasive and authoritative in your communication, and others often seek your advice. You may have a fear of others learning too much about you and prefer to keep to yourself.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou prefer to learn through observation rather than direct questioning. Your ability to see beyond the obvious enables you to grasp hidden meanings easily. Strive to trust others more and not always feel the need to be in control of your self-expression.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":4,\"title\":\"4th house\",\"influence\":\"home\",\"planet\":\"Moon    \",\"meaning\":\"emotions, property, relationship with mother\",\"hemisphere\":\"western, lower  \",\"description\":\"Located at the very bottom of the wheel, the 4th house determines your roots, family life, and childhood joys and sorrows. It reveals how attached you are to your past and how you prioritize family values. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign that rules this house in your chart for insight into your relationship with parents, how you might act as a parent, and what brings you a sense of security.\",\"zone\":\"the first 1/3 of the circle    \",\"type\":\"corner  \",\"axis\":\" 4/10\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"Your personal life and family are your top priorities. You take pride in creating a harmonious and loving home for yourself and your loved ones. You are naturally protective of your privacy, heritage, and personal relationships.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust remember to find a healthy balance between defending your boundaries and opening up to others. While you build a secure foundation for yourself and your loved ones, try not to be too defensive.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You crave a sense of belonging but may struggle to find it. You may frequently change residences or make changes in your home, searching for that perfect feeling. But true emotional stability comes from within, not exterior circumstances. Some parts of you may have a hard time maturing emotionally and taking care of yourself.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may have a strong attachment to your past and traditions. Learning to let go and focus on the present will lead to personal growth and inner stability.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have an imaginative mind, always coming up with unique ideas and plans. Your thoughts are subjective and sometimes biased, but you love to keep a lively and intellectual atmosphere in your home.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a great memory and are interested in history, psychology, and politics. You are not quick to accept new ideas and can be quite old-fashioned in your thinking.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"The balance, beauty, and harmony you seek in your home life are reflected in the way you decorate and take care of your space. You appreciate quality and comfort and have a sentimental and nurturing way of expressing your love.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may become overly attached to a partner, but when you give your heart, you do it with genuine emotion. Your parents' marriage has a strong influence on your own partnering skills and parenting style.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"Your nurturing style may be unconventional and different from what others expect. You may be a loving and caring nurturer, but your independence and desire for freedom may also cause you to withdraw and keep your distance at times.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour childhood may have had an unpredictability or lack of emotional support that shaped your parenting or nurturing style. Despite this, you always have the best intentions, even if others see you as erratic or inconsistent.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"Family is everything to you, and you will fiercely protect and defend your loved ones. You may have buried anger and find it difficult to express your emotions directly. Your loved ones may bring out your passive-aggressive tendencies.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour home life is lively and intense, with a lot of energy and perhaps arguments. You enjoy domestic activities and may take on a leadership role at home. Your actions are guided by your gut instincts, and you don't like being manipulated or controlled.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"Family and close loved ones hold a special place in your heart, and you thrive in a warm and loving home environment. You likely grew up with strong moral values, making you feel grounded and secure in your identity.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour dream home is likely grand and spacious, and you have a deep appreciation for the phrase \\\"home is where the heart is.\\\" Old age is expected to bring joy and fulfillment, thanks to your strong foundation and connections with loved ones.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"Your family life and memories of childhood may feel lacking in warmth and affection due to Saturn's influence. You may also have a sense of responsibility that impacts your nurturing abilities, making it feel more like a chore than something enjoyable.\\r\\n\\r\\nRecognizing this attitude and making a conscious effort to enjoy yourself and your family can help you break free from the seriousness and connect more deeply with loved ones. Show your patriotism and loyalty to your community with quiet pride.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"Your childhood may have been tumultuous, with a confusing or absent parental figure. This may have made it difficult for you to establish a strong sense of self and a sense of home. It's important to face these past experiences in order to find peace and stability.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a strong longing for a nurturing and loving family environment, and you may create this for yourself by extending your definition of family. You may also struggle with setting boundaries and giving too much of yourself without receiving love and support in return.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 4\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"Early experiences may have caused you to be secretive or self-protective. A parent or parental figure may have instilled guilt or shame surrounding your origins. Though you may feel proud of your roots, a fear of change or loss may be deeply ingrained in you.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour upbringing may have encouraged a love for psychology, and you may have grown up learning to look beyond the surface of things. You may also hold on to intense fears or obsessions from your childhood, influencing your attitudes toward your home and family.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":5,\"title\":\"5th house\",\"influence\":\"creativity \",\"planet\":\"Sun \",\"meaning\":\"intelligence, children \",\"hemisphere\":\"western, lower       \",\"description\":\"The 5th house is all about what makes you feel good, whether it's orgasms, attention, or the fulfilling work on a creative project. It reveals how passionate you are about life's joys and how you approach your hobbies. \\r\\nLook at the sign that rules this house in your chart for clues on how you incorporate playfulness into your life, express your artistic visions, and indulge in joyful activities.\",\"zone\":\"second 1/3 of the circle   \",\"type\":\"corner  \",\"axis\":\"5/11\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You love being in the spotlight and being recognized for your creative talents. Your joyful and fun-loving nature makes you stand out and attract attention effortlessly. You are likely to have a flair for drama and sports.\\r\\n\\r\\nBut do not bother to always demand center stage, as your natural charm will shine through without trying too hard. Instead, find creative outlets to express your emotions and take pride in your unconventional approach to life.<br>\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You enjoy sharing intense emotional experiences with loved ones and have a flair for drama. Your romantic relationships may go through many changes, but you form strong attachments to children. You are emotionally expressive and may act out your feelings or exaggerate them.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou also have a vivid imagination and artistic talents. Others are drawn to your childlike openness and playfulness, but be careful not to take unnecessary risks.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"Your communication style is a form of creative expression for you. You are quick-witted, funny, and often the life of the party. You also love playing games, making jokes, and entertaining others.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn relationships, you are attracted to those who share your intellectual curiosity and enjoy stimulating conversations. However, you may also have a tendency to exaggerate or make promises you can't keep.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You have been a hopeless romantic, drawn to love and all its pleasures since an early age. Your playful and sensual nature makes it easy for you to attract romantic attention.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou strongly appreciate beauty in all forms and may incorporate it into your ideal dates. There is a dramatic flair to your love life, as you both charm and get easily charmed by others.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"You have a natural talent for breaking the mold and bringing creativity to everything you do. In relationships, you crave excitement and may find yourself drawn to older or unconventional partners. Love, for you, is an adventure to be embraced.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a unique and unpredictable approach to life and may find yourself drawn to unconventional hobbies. Your offbeat lifestyle may puzzle others, but it brings you joy and satisfaction.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You strongly desire fun and pleasure and are not afraid to go after it directly and spontaneously. Sports and activities with an element of risk are especially appealing to you.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou put a lot of energy into pursuing your passions and are always up for a challenge. Your hobbies are likely to be very active and engaging, and you may even enjoy performing or putting on a show.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You have a generous and warm heart, particularly when it comes to children and romantic relationships. You may find success in creative fields, entertainment, or anything that brings joy and happiness to others.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a natural ability to teach and enlighten others, making learning enjoyable and fun. Your love for life and positive outlook make you popular among friends and a favorite among children.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"The fifth house is all about self-expression and spontaneity, but Saturn's presence here may hinder your ability to have fun and let go. You may come across as a \\\"party pooper,\\\" but you can turn this around by engaging in activities with a cause or purpose.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn romance, try to let your date lead and loosen up a little. Try to find a balance between work and play to avoid becoming overly stressed and having fun without having to justify it.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You are a creative and imaginative individual with a flair for drama. You may excel in the performing arts or have a natural talent for working with and caring for children. Your romantic life may be full of fantasy and idealization, so it's important to stay grounded in reality to avoid disappointment.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may attract chaotic or secretive relationships if you are not spiritually content within yourself. Be careful not to try and save others or hold them to unrealistic expectations. Balance your love for drama with a healthy dose of practicality.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 5\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have a strong creative drive and pour your soul into your art or hobbies. You take pride in your creations and may also invest your ego into them. In love, you seek deep and intense connections and are not satisfied with anything superficial.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you are not owning this energy, you may attract intense or controlling romantic partners who reflect your hidden fears of betrayal or loss. Your attitude toward play and recreation may also be serious and intense, often driven by a fear of losing control.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":6,\"title\":\"6th house\",\"influence\":\"daily life \",\"planet\":\"Mercury \",\"meaning\":\"health, enemies, difficulties    \",\"hemisphere\":\"western, lower      \",\"description\":\"The 6th house is all about your approach to everyday tasks, self-care routines, and service to others. It shows how you manage your work responsibilities, maintain your well-being, and find fulfillment in supporting those around you. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign ruling this house in your chart to understand your attitude toward work, health habits, and willingness to help others.\",\"zone\":\"second 1/3 of the circle       \",\"type\":\"cadent  \",\"axis\":\"6/12\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"Your identity is closely tied to your work and the services you offer to others. You feel most fulfilled when you're busy and productive, so it is important to choose a career or job that allows you to express yourself and develop your skills.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, be careful not to put your worth solely in the hands of others, as your health may suffer when you feel under-appreciated. Remember to prioritize your needs, and don't let criticism break you. Your motivation to do a good job should come from within.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You have a strong emotional need to be productive, organized, and useful. You may change jobs pretty often in search of the perfect fit, but learning to find joy in daily tasks can help. You are also very perceptive of your health and may experience minor ailments frequently.\\r\\n\\r\\nTaking care of others is an instinct for you, but be mindful not to overstep boundaries or try to help people who don't want to be helped.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a sharp and detail-oriented mind that is always busy. You excel at organizing, making lists, and finding solutions to problems. Others rely on you for your helpfulness and practical advice. However, this can make you prone to nervousness or overthinking.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may have a tendency toward hypochondria, as you notice every little ache and pain. Nervous tension could also contribute to health issues for you.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You show your love and affection through practical actions and service to your partner. You are always available and willing to help, often putting their needs before your own. You have a talent for finding order and harmony in daily routines and enjoy taking care of your loved ones.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, be careful not to settle for a relationship out of convenience or fear of not finding better. You have a tendency to underestimate your desires and worth.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"Your work style is likely to be influenced by science and technology, and you may find traditional jobs to be too confining for your freedom-loving nature. You are creative with daily tasks and seek to do things differently and more efficiently.\\r\\n\\r\\nHealthwise, you keep up with changing trends but also have your own unique views. You may not be afraid to challenge the experts and have your own unconventional methods for maintaining wellness.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You have a strong work ethic and put a lot of energy into your tasks, sometimes to the point of exhaustion. You thrive when working independently or in a leadership role, but you may become impatient if others don't work as hard as you.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour organizational skills are top-notch, and you excel at analyzing and improving processes. Just be careful not to get too worked up or defensive when others criticize your work or interfere with your routine.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You have a strong sense of morality and treat others with respect and fairness, even in business. Your honest and genuine approach may not always bring immediate success, but it builds trust and loyalty in the long run. You may find fulfillment in helping those in need. You have a strong work ethic and enjoy being of service to others.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, be mindful of overindulging in rich foods, as your love for pleasure and luxury may affect your health. Overall, you find great satisfaction and joy in your daily routines and work.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"Saturn feels right at home in this house, which represents your attitude toward work, service, and health. You may be a workaholic and struggle to prioritize your well-being over responsibilities, leading to mental and physical strain.\\r\\n\\r\\nBut with awareness, you can avoid falling into the trap of living to work and instead focus on a healthy work-life balance. Be mindful of not becoming too consumed with health and wellness, and remember to have fun and take care of yourself.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You may have a tendency to overlook details and routine tasks, preferring to follow your own ideals and philosophies. This can create chaos and guilt in your daily life, so it's important to find a balance between following your dreams and staying organized.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour sensitivity and tendency to avoid confrontation may also lead to health issues or difficulty setting boundaries. Take care of yourself by finding alternative health methods and learning to say no when necessary. You may also have a strong connection with animals and enjoy caring for them.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 6\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have a strong work ethic and can become obsessed with solving problems. You may also be overly private or attached to your work, often resentful of others trying to control your schedule. Research and analysis energize you, and you work tirelessly to find solutions.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may be interested in alternative therapies and deeply understand the mind-body connection, which makes you a skilled researcher in these areas. Balance is key for you, as you may struggle with fear of criticism and a tendency to overwork yourself.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":7,\"title\":\"7th house\",\"influence\":\" partnership  \",\"planet\":\"Venus \",\"meaning\":\"marriage, relationship, the business partnership\",\"hemisphere\":\"western, upper   \",\"description\":\"The 7th house governs your long-term relationships, both personal and professional. It sheds light on how you view partnerships, your approach to collaboration, and your ability to compromise. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign governing this house in your chart to gain insight into your approach to friendships, marriage, and professional connections.\",\"zone\":\"second 1/3 of the circle            \",\"type\":\"corner  \",\"axis\":\"6/12\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You pride yourself on your ability to negotiate, compromise, and create harmony in your relationships. You are motivated to become well-liked, and you are especially sensitive to rejection. Having a partner is important to you, as you feel incomplete without one.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour social skills are your superpower, but don't let them overshadow your true self. Seek peaceful relationships, but don't rely on them for your self-esteem. Also, avoid becoming too dependent on others' opinions of you.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"Relationships are essential for your emotional well-being, and you may struggle with being alone. You are always learning and growing through your partnerships but may have a tendency to jump from one to the next without taking enough time for yourself in between.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are adaptable and likable, but be aware of becoming overly dependent on a partner or assuming they will treat you the same way as you treat them. Remember to take care your own needs, not just those of your partner.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a love for discussion and debate, especially when it comes to understanding yourself and others. You often play devil's advocate, seeing the other side of the argument. However, making decisions and sticking to one opinion may be a challenge.\\r\\n\\r\\nCommunication is important to you, especially in relationships. You thrive in one-on-one conversations and love to share your thoughts and ideas. You may become bored in partnerships if communication breaks down.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"Relationships are everything to you, and you have a hard time imagining being alone. You strive for harmony and avoid dominating your partner. Your naturally agreeable and charming nature draws people to you.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a strong need for connection and may enter partnerships quickly, sometimes without being fully prepared. Be careful not to sacrifice your own needs for the sake of keeping the peace in a superficial relationship.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"In relationships, you may struggle with committing and prefer your independence over anything else. Your partners may find you unpredictable but also charming and genuine. You may see relationships as a necessary but not entirely comfortable part of life.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may be drawn to partners who value their personal freedom, similar to your desire for independence. Avoiding stagnancy and always seeking change and evolution is what drives you in relationships.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You thrive on excitement and challenges in your relationships and need a partner who can keep up with you. You are drawn to assertive and strong-willed individuals and may discover your own assertiveness through them.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a talent for mediation, counseling, and negotiating. Your assertiveness and ability to work with others can bring success in politics, law, or any collaborative ventures.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"Creating meaningful and equal partnerships is a top priority for you. You have a natural talent for mediation and negotiations, and legal matters may work in your favor. You value relationships and believe in fairness and balance.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour charm and graciousness can help you succeed in business and marriage. You have a deep desire to reach your goals and build a lasting legacy with your partner by your side.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You treat relationships like a business partnership, focusing on practicality and responsibility rather than affection and love. Your responsible attitude may attract serious, organized, and self-disciplined people into your life.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour reserved nature may make it difficult to form new relationships or commit to existing ones. But once in a partnership, you take your role as a reliable and devoted partner seriously.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You give more in a relationship than you take, often wearing rose-colored glasses to find your perfect soulmate. But this can lead to idealizing your partner and not seeing them for who they truly are.\\r\\n\\r\\nAs you search for a strong emotional connection with a partner, you may attract people who are unable to commit or who confuse you. It's important to take a step back and see your partner clearly rather than projecting your own desires onto them.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 7\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"When it comes to close relationships, power struggles and intense emotions are often part of the dynamic. You may crave a deep connection but also fear losing control in a partnership.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may attract intense and controlling people, and your own fear of betrayal and power can complicate things. However, with self-awareness, you can transform and have rewarding relationships.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":8,\"title\":\"8th house\",\"influence\":\"business\",\"planet\":\"Pluto\",\"meaning\":\"birth, death, power, inheritance\",\"hemisphere\":\"western, upper\",\"description\":\"The 8th house governs intense and transformative experiences, including sexuality, death, and spiritual renewal. It shows your capacity for deep change, your attitude toward intimate connections, and your approach to occultism. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign ruling this house in your chart to explore how you approach emotional transformation, intimacy, death, and rebirth.\",\"zone\":\"second 1/3 of the circle\",\"type\":\"following\",\"axis\":\"2/8\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You have a deep desire to explore and experience all that life has to offer. You are not satisfied with superficial experiences and are constantly seeking to go deeper and further. You have a magnetic energy and are drawn to mysterious subjects.\\r\\n\\r\\nAt some point in your life, self-improvement and personal growth will be a major focus for you. Embrace your fascination with the unknown and use your intense energy wisely.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You have a strong desire to push your emotional limits and explore taboo subjects. Be aware that this may manifest in extreme behavior, such as constantly changing sexual partners, as a way to cope with your own insecurities.\\r\\n\\r\\nThough you have a deep need for emotional intimacy, you may also struggle with trusting others and tend to keep yourself closed off. Your devoted nature can lead to intense loyalty in relationships but can also make it difficult to let others in.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have a great curiosity for all things mysterious, taboo, and psychological. You are skilled at analyzing and understanding people's motivations and may excel in fields such as finance or medicine. With your persuasive abilities, you have a powerful impact on others.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a knack for finding hidden meanings and creating strategic plans. However, be mindful of using your powers for good rather than manipulation.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You crave intensity in love and are not satisfied with shallow or superficial connections. You may have a fear of being vulnerable, which can lead to possessive or jealous tendencies. When you do fall in love, you give yourself completely and expect the same from your partner.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour alluring and charming nature may mask a deeper, more passionate side. You are drawn to the taboo and may have a strong interest in love, romance, and eroticism. People are easily intrigued by your intense energy.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"You love change and believe that it brings growth and excitement to life. You enjoy reinventing yourself and embracing new ideas and experiences. However, your urge for change may be unsettling for others, and they may struggle to keep up with your fast pace.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour impatience with the status quo can sometimes make you overlook other people's emotions. Remember to be considerate of others and their feelings, even when you are eager for change. After all, your intentions are always good!\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You can lack passion in your early years, but when it hits, it's powerful and contagious. You excel at deep and focused work, which makes you an excellent researcher, investigator, or psychologist. Your intuition runs deep, but you may struggle with feelings of guilt or fear.\\r\\n\\r\\nTrust can be an issue, but once it's earned, you are fiercely loyal. Keeping your emotions buried can harm your health, so learning to express them directly is key.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You have a knack for problem-solving and uncovering hidden truths. You love diving deep into mysteries and using strategy to solve complex issues. Your natural generosity extends to your partner, both emotionally and materially.\\r\\n\\r\\nTaboos and the unknown don't faze you — in fact, they may intrigue you. You have a natural understanding of the deeper, darker parts of life and are not afraid to explore them.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You are highly motivated and determined to succeed in your personal and professional life. You have a strong sense of responsibility and may take on important roles in your family or community. Your disciplined approach helps you navigate intense and transformative experiences.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may have a fear of losing control, causing you to be guarded in your relationships. However, with time and patience, you can overcome these challenges and build deep and meaningful connections.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You have a strong spiritual longing and may experience psychic phenomena regularly. Your sexual fantasies and desires may be unusual, and you may feel unfulfilled in relationships.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn order to find true balance and satisfaction, it's important to be selective in choosing sexual partners and to be more disciplined with your finances. You may have a tendency to be taken advantage of in relationships, whether it be financially or emotionally.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 8\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You are fascinated with all things hidden and mysterious, which can lead to unique and intense experiences. You have a strong intuition and can cut through appearances to the truth.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour sexual relationships may also be intense and complicated, as you are drawn to deep intimacy yet fear vulnerability. Learning to understand and manage control issues is important for growth.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":9,\"title\":\"9th house\",\"influence\":\"travel\",\"planet\":\"Jupiter  \",\"meaning\":\"luck, ideas, teachers, father  \",\"hemisphere\":\"western, upper   \",\"description\":\"The 9th house represents your worldview and belief systems, as well as travel and education. It reflects your search for meaning, your philosophical principles, and how you expand your mind through learning and exploration. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign ruling this house in your chart to explore your sense of wanderlust, how you soak up knowledge and approach philosophical conversations.\",\"zone\":\"third 1/3 of a circle  \",\"type\":\"cadent  \",\"axis\":\"3/9\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"Your curiosity and thirst for knowledge sets you apart from others. You have high ideals and are always looking ahead to what the future holds. Your restless nature can sometimes make you seem like a wanderer, but you are always searching for new opportunities for growth.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust make sure to avoid being overly righteous when sharing your beliefs. When used positively, your curiosity and adventurous spirit can make you open-minded and accepting of others.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You have a strong longing for adventure and growth beyond your daily routines. While it's okay to dream of faraway places, be careful not to discount or overlook the joy and opportunities in your current circumstances.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour constantly seeking nature can lead to restlessness and discontentment. Learning to appreciate the present and setting heartfelt goals for yourself will bring more fulfillment than constantly chasing after the next big thing.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You have an unquenchable thirst for knowledge and enjoy learning for the sake of learning. Sharing ideas and philosophies with others brings you great joy. You have a knack for seeing the big picture and may have a talent for languages.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may struggle with details but excel at finding quick solutions to problems. Your love for information inspires others to take action and make changes. You may also have a fascination with different cultures and enjoy traveling.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You are attracted to people from different cultural backgrounds and love embarking on new adventures with a partner. You value your freedom and personal growth and won't be happy in a relationship that feels limiting.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhile you have high ideals in love, you can sometimes be swayed by momentary pleasures. Be aware of your tendency to become dissatisfied in relationships and remember to appreciate what you have.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"Your independent nature and fascination with new ideas and philosophies make you a natural explorer. You enjoy traveling, meeting new people, and expanding your mind through education and self-discovery. Traditional and conservative ways of thinking may not align with your beliefs.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou reject the limitations of the world and constantly seek new ways to expand your horizons. Your unique and creative perspective can bring fresh ideas to any intellectual pursuit.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"A sense of adventure and a love for debate and learning define you. But beware of taking disagreements personally and becoming aggressive or hurt. Be open to different perspectives and approach discussions with a level head.\\r\\n\\r\\nSex is seen as a playful and energetic activity for you, and you may have a direct and blunt approach to it. Your passion and humor are irresistible to others. You have a curious and restless mind, always seeking new experiences and pushing boundaries.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"Your appetite for knowledge and wisdom is insatiable. You love sharing your wisdom and beliefs with others and may even find success as a teacher or mentor. Freedom of movement and expression are crucial to your happiness.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are an adventurer at heart and enjoy traveling and learning about foreign cultures. Your open-mindedness and thirst for new experiences inspire others.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You approach life with a practical and grounded mind, lacking interest in abstract or imaginative ideas. You may struggle to open your mind to new concepts and may reject them without giving them a chance.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour practical thinking can be a great asset, but don't let it close you off from new experiences or limit your potential for growth. Be open to new ideas and encourage others to share their perspectives with you.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You have unwavering faith in the universe and believe that anything is possible. However, this can lead to neglecting practical responsibilities and chasing unrealistic dreams.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour spiritual beliefs are strong, but it's important to think critically and not blindly follow any concepts or religions. Keep your larger goals in check and stay grounded while maintaining your ideals.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 9\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have strong and well-researched opinions and enjoy sharing them, even if it leads to debates. You have a deep curiosity for knowledge and adventure and may even seek out unique experiences.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour strong beliefs and need for control can sometimes cause issues in your relationships. However, when balanced, you can be an inspiring teacher or speaker.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":10,\"title\":\"10th house\",\"influence\":\"career\",\"planet\":\"Saturn\",\"meaning\":\"status, honor, reputation \",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, upper  \",\"description\":\"The 10th house defines your professional life, reputation, and aspirations. It spotlights your career ambitions, approach to authority, and drive for success. \\r\\nLook at the zodiac sign ruling this house in your chart for insights into your approach to career achievements, work ethic, and how you present yourself in the public eye.\",\"zone\":\"third 1/3 of a circle  \",\"type\":\"сorner \",\"axis\":\"4/10\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You are a natural-born leader who craves success and achievement. Following orders isn't your style — you'd rather be the one giving them. Look for a career that puts you in charge and allows you to flex your ambition at full throttle.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust be careful not to let your drive for power consume your true self. Remember to balance your need for recognition with staying true to your authentic identity. Use your ambitions and your need for authority without going overboard.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"Your emotional needs revolve around recognition, achievement, and popularity. While you may be quite charismatic, it can take time for you to settle into a structured and responsible life that brings true emotional fulfillment.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may struggle with decision-making, as your choices are often influenced by your emotions and the expectations of others. Remember to set your own heartfelt goals and not just follow the desires and expectations of those around you.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You possess a natural skill with language and often use it in your profession. You have a commanding presence and excel at communicating and negotiating with authority figures.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour career may be ever-changing, with multiple jobs or frequent changes in direction, as you thrive on new challenges and need variety to stay stimulated. Also, your ability to bring fresh perspectives to conversations or projects is highly valued.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"You have a natural charm and charisma that attracts admirers from near and far. However, you may struggle with finding deep, meaningful connections due to maintaining a charming yet distant aura. Be careful not to become too focused on seeking others' approval or attention.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour creative instincts are strong, and you may thrive in artistic pursuits or hobbies. You also have a natural talent for organizing social events and bringing people together. Don't be afraid to let your inner child come out to play.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"You value your independence greatly and may struggle with conforming to a specific career or role. You have a creative and competent approach to your work but dislike hierarchies and power dynamics. You prefer a flat and equal structure.\\r\\n\\r\\nStatus and reputation are not important to you, and you may choose a less traditional or unconventional career path. You have a unique approach to leadership, which may be challenging for others to understand at first.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You are determined and driven in your career pursuits. You thrive in leadership roles and prefer to be in control of your own timeline. In relationships, you are usually the one to take charge and plan activities.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour competitive streak and desire for independence make you well-suited for careers where you can be a pioneer or have a certain level of freedom. You value personal achievements and may not always seek approval from others.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"You have a natural talent for leadership and a positive, go-getter attitude that helps you achieve success in your career. Others may see you as lucky, but in reality, it's your hard work and ethical nature that brings you opportunities.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou value success and recognition and are motivated to leave a lasting mark on the world. Your sense of responsibility and resourcefulness set you apart from others in your industry.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You take your career and reputation very seriously, shouldering immense responsibilities with ease. You may feel like you are constantly under a microscope, which can make you defensive and self-conscious.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may feel the pressure to excel and fear failure, causing you to be cautious in your career choices. But your practical nature can lead you to success if you learn to balance it with taking some risks. Build a strong foundation, but don't be afraid to step out of your comfort zone.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"Your intuition and creativity are huge assets in your career, especially in fields such as art or charity work. However, if you allow your fears and doubts to take over, you may struggle to find your calling or establish a reputation.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt's important to have a clear direction and believe in yourself in order to succeed. Don't let others take credit for your work and don't be afraid to promote yourself and your talents.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 10\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You have a unique and powerful presence that makes you stand out in your career. Your ambition and determination can lead to success, but you may also face power struggles in the workplace.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a strong sense of responsibility but may not enjoy being subordinate to others. Your relationship with your father or authority figures may also be intense and shape your professional path.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":11,\"title\":\"11th house\",\"influence\":\"groups\",\"planet\":\"Uranus \",\"meaning\":\" profit, business, ambition \",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, upper  \",\"description\":\"The 11th house governs your social network, ideals, and humanitarian efforts. It unveils your involvement in groups, your vision for the future, and your stance on social causes. Look at the sign ruling this house in your chart to unveil your approach to activism, social justice, and your role in community advancement.\",\"zone\":\"third 1/3 of a circle  \",\"type\":\"following  \",\"axis\":\"5/11 \",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You are a true humanitarian at heart. You have a strong sense of social justice and strive to treat everyone with fairness and respect. Your individuality is rooted in being different from the norm, and you reject prejudices and biases.\\r\\n\\r\\nStatus and popularity hold little importance to you compared to being part of a diverse group. You find your purpose in contributing to a community or a movement that promotes positive change.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You thrive on a sense of belonging and support from friends and groups. Your social life may fluctuate in reflection of your changing emotions, but ultimately, you find emotional fulfillment through your involvement in causes and communities.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour dreams and aspirations tend to be altruistic and community-oriented, but you may struggle with wavering goals and finding lasting happiness. Remember to take time for yourself and stay grounded in your own needs and desires.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You are endlessly interested in people, group dynamics, and society. You are drawn to individuals with unique ideas and enjoy intellectual discussions. You have a strong sense of fairness and are always looking toward the future.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may experience changes in your goals and the people you associate with. While you have a strong desire to help others, be cautious of attracting toxic or untrustworthy friends.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"Your independence makes it difficult for you to fully connect with any group or social circle. You have idealistic goals and may be seen as superior or dismissive by those who compromise their beliefs for the sake of fitting in.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour wit and charm can win people over, but you may come across as aloof and erratic in group situations. You value honesty and simplicity in relationships and tend to form deep connections with those who share your ideals and passions.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You are a natural-born leader and enjoy organizing events and activities. Your friends admire your helpfulness and action-oriented attitude. You may have trouble connecting deeply with others and prefer to maintain a bit of distance.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou have a strong sense of justice and may be drawn to fighting for important causes. Your friendships are likely to be passionate and may have conflicts at times due to your assertive nature.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"Your social life is incredibly important to you, and you take pleasure in connecting with others through teams, groups, and community involvement. Your friends can be influential and helpful to your success.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour passion for humanitarianism and progress drives you to be open-minded and tolerant of others. You may find success in areas such as activism, technology, and humanitarian work.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"Socially conscious and driven, you have a deep desire to make a positive impact on your community or the world. However, you may struggle with feelings of isolation or being an outsider, leading you to value deep, intimate friendships over large social circles.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour strong sense of responsibility can also extend to your social connections, potentially bringing a sense of heaviness or duty to group activities. Finding a balance between your own needs and the needs of the greater good will be key to your success.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You have strong, idealistic views and are always accepting and accommodating in your friendships. While this makes you a great friend, be careful not to be taken advantage of or let down by unrealistic expectations.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou may also struggle to pinpoint your deepest wishes and may feel unsatisfied once you reach a goal. Be open to unique and creative friendships, but remember to set boundaries and be clear in your communication.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You take your friendships and group associations very seriously and may even experience intense power struggles. You have a strong sense of justice and believe in the power of the collective to affect change.\\r\\n\\r\\nLater in life, you may become motivated to make a positive impact on the world. However, be careful not to be influenced by others who may try to control your power and beliefs.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 11\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"Friendship is a key aspect of your romantic relationships. You are attracted to unique and unconventional qualities in a partner. Group activities may be a way for you to meet potential lovers.\\r\\nCreativity and playfulness are important to you, and you may find yourself drawn to partners who share these traits. However, be cautious of jumping into relationships without thinking about the responsibility they may bring.\\r\\n\"}]},{\"house_number\":12,\"title\":\"12th house\",\"influence\":\"selfishness\",\"planet\":\"Neptune \",\"meaning\":\"loss, expense, sex  \",\"hemisphere\":\"eastern, upper \",\"description\":\"The 12th house is related to spirituality and is often called the celestial house. It reveals your attitude toward the divine and how much you rely on intuition in your life. \\r\\nLook at the sign ruling this house in your chart to uncover your connection to spirituality, psychic abilities, karmic patterns, and unconscious motivations.\",\"zone\":\" third 1/3 of a circle \",\"type\":\"cadent  \",\"axis\":\"6/12\",\"house_in_planets\":[{\"title\":\"Sun in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"sun\",\"description\":\"You have an introspective nature and need a lot of alone time to recharge. Stepping into the limelight may not come naturally to you, but when you do, you tend to hide behind a mask. Creative hobbies bring you the most fulfillment — it's where you truly shine.\\r\\n\\r\\nBut don't let your imagination make you feel too isolated. Embrace your alone time, but don't forget to step out into the world as well.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Moon in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"moon\",\"description\":\"You have a deep emotional connection to all things ethereal and spiritual. However, your heightened sensitivity can lead to delayed reactions or feeling out of touch with your own emotions.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt's important for you to have frequent moments of solitude to recharge, but be mindful of isolating yourself too much. You have a strong desire to help and care for others, but it's essential to take good care of your own emotional needs.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mercury in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"mercury\",\"description\":\"You may struggle with self-expression, especially as a child. You are a trustworthy confidant and keep secrets well. Overthinking and analyzing instinctual feelings can cause you to doubt your intuition and have trouble acting on it.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are drawn to symbolism and emotions rather than hard facts. You learn best through visual or imaginative methods. Learning to communicate effectively can help you overcome feelings of guilt and attract more positive experiences.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Uranus in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"uranus\",\"description\":\"You have a deep desire for personal freedom and impact on the world but may not always express or articulate this desire. You may quietly support causes or individuals that align with your beliefs or search for ways to make the world a better place.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn relationships, you seek those who value freedom and creativity. You may find comfort in the company of artistic or spiritual individuals. You have a deep intuition and may be drawn to careers in science or technology as they push the limits of the known world.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Mars in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"mars\",\"description\":\"You may struggle with asserting yourself and may lack confidence in your abilities. However, with experience, you will learn to work with this energy and use it to your advantage. Your creativity and resourcefulness are key strengths.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou tend to put others' needs before your own but may secretly become angry or resentful. Overcoming these feelings and learning to prioritize your desires will lead to a more fulfilling life.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Jupiter in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"jupiter\",\"description\":\"This position of Jupiter is often referred to as the \\\"guardian angel\\\" - you have an inborn faith in the universe and may feel like something is always there to save you in tough times. Solitude, meditation, and spiritual practices bring you inner peace and rejuvenation.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou are merciful and generous, often giving anonymously. You have a deep understanding of the unseen and are not afraid to explore the mysteries of life. Trust your intuition, as it will guide you on the right path.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Saturn in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"saturn\",\"description\":\"You may struggle to assert yourself and may lack confidence in your abilities. However, with experience, you can learn to work with this energy and use it to your advantage. Your creativity and resourcefulness are key strengths.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou tend to put others' needs before your own but may secretly become angry or resentful. Overcoming these feelings and learning to prioritize your desires will lead to a more fulfilling life. Embrace your inner wisdom and intuition, and trust in your ability to navigate the mysteries of life. Let go of guilt and fear, and open up to others for support and growth.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Neptune in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"neptune\",\"description\":\"You possess deep intuition and inner strength that can surprise others. You may have difficulty expressing your empathetic nature, which can leave you feeling guilty.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt's important to trust in yourself and your spirituality, or you may resort to escapism and avoid dealing with issues. Embrace your faith, and it will guide you through life's changes.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Pluto in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"pluto\",\"description\":\"You are drawn to exploring your inner psyche and understanding others' motivations. You may have a strong intuition and a natural ability to heal and support others.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, you may keep many of your own secrets and emotions hidden, which can impact your well-being. Learning to open up and communicate can bring growth and prevent self-sabotage.\\r\\n\"},{\"title\":\"Venus in House 12\",\"planet_id\":\"venus\",\"description\":\"When it comes to love, you are all in. You can easily become enmeshed in a romantic partner's emotions and may struggle with setting boundaries. This can leave you feeling vulnerable and taken advantage of.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou long for a deep and spiritual connection in your relationships, and may be drawn to more unconventional forms of love and partnership. However, be sure to balance your needs to avoid becoming lost in a tumultuous sea of emotions.\\r\\n\"}]}]"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:48:37.813Z"
      },
