            "text": "{\"id\":59615,\"soulmate\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/soulmate_report/64c41ff9-3ac2-42e8-9f19-1601d023e5ae.jpg\",\"charts\":{\"your_chart\":{\"moon_sign\":\"aries\",\"sun_sign\":\"scorpio\",\"ascendant\":\"gemini\"},\"soulmate_chart\":{\"moon_sign\":\"leo\",\"sun_sign\":\"pisces\",\"ascendant\":\"libra\"},\"why_you_resonate\":{\"sun_text\":\"An unspoken emotional understanding. You resonate on a deep, intuitive level, validating each other's feelings without words.\",\"moon_text\":\"You find comfort in action and growth. Emotionally, you both need enthusiasm, making your private world dynamic and joy-filled.\",\"ascendant_text\":\"Effortless social flow. You click immediately, moving through social circles with a shared wit and approachable charm.\"},\"soulmate_energy\":{\"is_generated\":true,\"text\":\"With the compassionate depth of Pisces, a Leo moon brings heartfelt generosity and radiant confidence, while a Libra rising offers graceful diplomacy and polished social ease. Together they value emotional safety, creative intimacy, and balanced partnership—an empathetic, warm soulmate who cultivates beauty, loyalty, and harmonious shared life.\"},\"you_in_this_dynamic\":{\"is_generated\":true,\"text\":\"By offering gentle, imaginative faith in your aims, their compassionate, dream-weaving support validates your Scorpio heart; their theatrical, generous comfort soothes your Aries moon's fierce pulses, and their poised, harmonizing presence reflects and boosts your Gemini rising's quicksilver confidence to speak, charm, and connect freely.\"},\"where_you_met\":{\"sun_text\":\"Soulful places like art galleries, intimate music venues, or anywhere near the ocean.\",\"moon_text\":\"Places to let loose, such as karaoke bars, comedy clubs, or dynamic fitness studios.\",\"ascendant_text\":\"Crowded social events, art openings, or pop-up markets where mingling is easy.\"},\"chemistry\":{\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"text\":\"A spiritual merger. This connection goes beyond the physical; it feels fated. You dissolve into one another. The dynamic is magical and all-consuming. You handle the deep waters of emotion together, finding a level of intimacy and trust that you cannot find with anyone else.\",\"percent\":99},\"emotions\":{\"sign\":\"leo\",\"text\":\"Your emotions flare up instantly, and a Leo Moon is the only one who doesn't try to dim your light. They shower you with warmth and attention when you're upset. In this connection, you feel like a star, and your partner takes pride in your raw honesty instead of judging your temper.\",\"percent\":97},\"harmony\":{\"sign\":\"libra\",\"text\":\"You are the couple everyone wants to talk to. The vibe is flirtatious, witty, and lighthearted. You charm the room with words, and they charm it with grace. It's a relationship free of heaviness, filled with parties, culture, and endless fascinating dialogue.\",\"percent\":95},\"overall\":{\"is_generated\":true,\"text\":\"Your Scorpio Sun and their Piscean Sun send you on moonlit pilgrimages—diving into hidden towns, soulful art, and quiet rites that rewire the heart.  \\nEmotion is the map; intimacy the destination.  \\nAt home, Aries and Leo Moons make the rooms a sunlit, theatrical sanctuary—sudden music, bold breakfasts, a shelf of trophies and postcards.  \\nIt's impulsive and regal: playful duels, dramatic storytelling, and ceremonial small victories.  \\nWith Gemini Rising beside Libra Rising you are the charming, eloquent pair who can turn any stranger into a confidant.  \\nYou move through life like a whispered secret—stylish, witty, and quietly magnetic.\"}},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 07:06:18\"}"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:48:40.513Z"
      },
