            "size": 961,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":45827021,\"date\":\"2026-02-28\",\"period\":\"day\",\"data\":{\"powerAndFocus\":\"ambition, responsibility, growth\",\"troubles\":\"emotional tension, miscommunication, impatience\",\"header\":\"Navigating emotional energies\",\"blocks\":[{\"title\":\"Harness Your Ambition\",\"text\":\"As Mars aligns with your natal placement, focus on channeling energy into your projects. This is a great period for tangible achievements, yet avoid rushing decisions. Instead, set practical goals while considering emotional well-being.\"},{\"title\":\"Stay Grounded in Emotions\",\"text\":\"Jupiter's square to the Moon could trigger unanticipated emotional responses. Take a moment to reflect on your feelings before reacting. In relationships, prioritize open communication to avoid misunderstandings during this time.\"},{\"title\":\"Tip\",\"text\":\"Limit impulsivity by grounding yourself in nature or engaging in a calming routine. Reflecting on your ambitions will help navigate the energetic shifts.\"}]}}]"
