          "content": {
            "size": 1048,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":45891320,\"date\":\"2026-03-01\",\"period\":\"day\",\"data\":{\"powerAndFocus\":\"ambition, practicality, resilience\",\"troubles\":\"emotional upheavals, misunderstandings, reluctance\",\"header\":\"Navigating emotional currents\",\"blocks\":[{\"title\":\"Understanding Your Feelings\",\"text\":\"Today, your emotions may feel more intense due to the Moon influencing your inner world. You could sense the tension from your professional endeavors demanding focus. Engage in careful reflection, especially during workplace interactions, to prevent misunderstandings.\"},{\"title\":\"Fostering Connections\",\"text\":\"With the Moon's positive trine to your natal Sun, developing deeper connections in personal relationships is favored now. Trust your instincts as you open up to loved ones, but avoid being overly critical—let warmth guide your conversations.\"},{\"title\":\"Tip\",\"text\":\"Take a moment for self-care. A short walk or a journaling session can help you process your emotions constructively. Connect with your inner thoughts and let go of burdens you don't need.\"}]}}]"
