            "size": 36975,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":62,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Aries have a strong and confident personality. Retaining their dignity in any relationship is essential to them. Although they won’t try to suppress another person, they like to compete sometimes, just for fun. People born under this sign are known to be passionate about life. That’s why the Fire elements – Leo and Sagittarius – will get along really well with Aries. But don’t forget that opposites attract. Hot-tempered Aries and careful Libra balance each other out, however, you should be extra cautious with this kind of union.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aries\",\"signs\":[\"leo\",\"libra\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":1175,\"dislikes\":130},{\"id\":63,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"​Best couple for Aries​\",\"description\":\"<p>Aries and Aquarius can never get bored together, that’s why their relationship is always exciting. They like trying new things and keep looking for unusual ways to spend time. Other couples can get tired of each other, but not these guys!</p><p>Leo will eagerly share your passion for life and help you experience unforgettable moments. You can rarely find such fiery passion in other couples!</p><p><br></p>\",\"sign\":\"aries\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":1079,\"dislikes\":232},{\"id\":64,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Marriage compatibility\",\"description\":\"<p>With Leo, you will achieve all your dreams, whether it’s about career or family. Spontaneity, adventurous spirit, and sincere emotions are essential for both of you. Leo and Aries can spend an incredible amount of time in bed. It’s a perfect couple!</p>\",\"sign\":\"aries\",\"signs\":[\"leo\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":847,\"dislikes\":112},{\"id\":65,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The Fire element represents energy, power, and life. It makes you move forward and stand your ground. Those who have a trigon of the Fire element in their horoscopes are confident, fearless, and have a versatile mind. They are enterprising and have excellent managerial skills. Their extraordinary energy helps them achieve their goals.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aries\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"leo\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":492,\"dislikes\":21},{\"id\":66,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Fire needs oxygen to burn. Same here: the Fire element meets the Air forming a dangerous, yet intriguing, connection. Aries often make impulsive decisions that lead to unexpected consequences. Libra, on the contrary, have a calm and balanced personality and tend to spend hours making plans. So such relationships can lead to endless fights and disagreements. However, let’s not forget that opposites attract. If a hot-tempered Aries and a tactful Libra find the way to balance each other out, this kind of relationship may become exciting and appealing for both of them!</p>\",\"sign\":\"aries\",\"signs\":[\"libra\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":670,\"dislikes\":62},{\"id\":67,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Taurus can be described as pragmatic and balanced people who prefer to have stable relationships. Therefore, it is great if, in the surrounding of close friends, there is such a zodiac sign as Capricorn. Both zodiac signs value emotional stability and practicality. Capricorns will always give an excellent piece of advice and will be happy to discuss any questions. If you want to get permanent pushing and feel the spirit of healthy competition, start your communication with Scorpio. Together with this sign, you will quickly achieve your goals and excellent results in life. It will be interesting for you to explore your creative and spiritual potential with Pisces.</p>\",\"sign\":\"taurus\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"scorpio\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":884,\"dislikes\":127},{\"id\":68,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Taurus\",\"description\":\"<p>Taurus and Cancer have a strong connection to each other both on the emotional and on the physical levels. They understand each other perfectly, which helps them to build strong and trustful relationships. This passionate couple knows how to burn feelings!</p>\",\"sign\":\"taurus\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":1139,\"dislikes\":223},{\"id\":69,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Marriage compatibility\",\"description\":\"<p>Taurus is a patient and trustful partner, who needs a long-term relationship. The best candidates for him will be representatives of the earth elements - Virgo and Capricorn. But before building a family, Taurus will undoubtedly check the partner for compliance with his life’s values. A sense of security and a peaceful environment at home is important to him.</p>\",\"sign\":\"taurus\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\",\"virgo\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":895,\"dislikes\":75},{\"id\":70,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>People whose horoscopes are expressed by the elements of the Earth normally have a practical approach to life. They are prudent, patient, and self-confident personalities. Earth analyzes, structures, and creates the foundation for the next actions. The people of this trigon set real goals and firmly go to them. Although they are careful and attentive, they can defend their interests, if necessary. The main principle of the Earth's trigon is stability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"taurus\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"virgo\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":379,\"dislikes\":26},{\"id\":71,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Each zodiac sign belongs to one of four elements: Water, Air, Earth, and Fire. If the partner has the same trigon with you, then such a relationship can be easy and pleasant. But, if it is the opposite sign of the zodiac, you may feel uncomfortable.\\r\\nThere are passion and emotions in the relation between Taurus and Scorpio. Both partners are jealous and often try to destroy each other's independence. Taurus will not have a scandal without good reason, because it prefers a calm and comfortable life. But Scorpio, whose mood changes all the time, will definitely try to find an excuse to do it. </p>\",\"sign\":\"taurus\",\"signs\":[\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":569,\"dislikes\":65},{\"id\":72,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Gemini prefers to have an active social life and to demonstrate its intelligence and a huge amount of knowledge. That is why they are attracted by Air signs, which can always communicate on any topic. Libra and Aquarius will understand the Gemini at a glance since they have a similar way of thinking and ideas. But Aries will be drawn into real adventures, but at the same time, it will respect the personal boundaries.</p>\",\"sign\":\"gemini\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"aries\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":1052,\"dislikes\":123},{\"id\":73,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Gemini\",\"description\":\"<p>An incredible and spiritual connection is formed between Gemini and Aquarius. It may seem that they have known each other for many years, even when they just have a first date! They harmoniously complement each other and like to spend time together, but at the same time, they understand the importance of personal space.</p>\",\"sign\":\"gemini\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":942,\"dislikes\":144},{\"id\":74,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>The best aphrodisiac for Gemini is the extraordinary mind of a partner. The value of intelligence and wit are the most important. Dynamic and active representatives of this zodiac sign are attracted by new meetings and experiences. Leo and Gemini will have a passionate and vivid relationship in which there will be no place for boredom. One should expect a powerful physical and psychological connection with air Aquarius. If you are looking for a more intellectual and emotional relationship, Libra is suitable.</p>\",\"sign\":\"gemini\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"leo\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":733,\"dislikes\":58},{\"id\":75,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The element of Air is considered to be the trigon of ideas and intelligence. People who belong to this element are constantly in search of new knowledge and sensations. The element of Air carries in itself a changing creative activity, giving to people such qualities as flexibility, liveliness, mobility of the mind and psycho, and insatiability. They do not like monotony since it depresses their psycho. The basic principles of a trigon are interconnection and exchange.</p>\",\"sign\":\"gemini\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"gemini\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":379,\"dislikes\":32},{\"id\":76,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Gemini and Sagittarius have a passion for new knowledge and travel. They are connected by a lively interest in different courses, entertainment, and cultural events. This couple will never get bored while learning and discovering the world.</p>\",\"sign\":\"gemini\",\"signs\":[\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":785,\"dislikes\":67},{\"id\":77,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Cancer wishes emotional security and deep relationships. Such a wonderful spiritual organization will be appreciated by Scorpions - with them you can work out all your hidden fears and learn how to trust other people. There is real synergy with Taurus! These zodiac signs have the same look at life: they try to achieve self-realization and perfection. You can get the perfect partnership with Capricorn because you can always find support and understanding from him.</p>\",\"sign\":\"cancer\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"scorpio\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":785,\"dislikes\":98},{\"id\":78,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\" Best couple for Cancer\",\"description\":\"<p>Taurus and Cancer have a strong connection to each other both on the emotional and on the physical levels. They understand each other perfectly, which helps them to build strong and trustful relationships. This passionate couple knows how to burn feelings!</p>\",\"sign\":\"cancer\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":661,\"dislikes\":134},{\"id\":79,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Patient and attentive Cancer loves to unusually care and is susceptible to external beauty. He needs to find a relationship in life in which he can fully trust his partner. Cancer can make a strong union with Taurus. Trust is the main part of a harmonious relationship for both zodiac signs. \\r\\n\\r\\nCancer will definitely feel calm and deep feelings with Scorpio. But you need to be careful: don’t go too far with the intensity of emotions. \\r\\n\\r\\nIt can be interesting to have a relationship with Pisces. Crazy erotic experiments and colorful dates will make the law of attraction to work for this couple! </p>\",\"sign\":\"cancer\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"taurus\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":517,\"dislikes\":56},{\"id\":80,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>Water is considered the trigon of sensations and feelings. Representatives of the water element have a strong connection with the unconscious mind. They are not interested in empty talking, which doesn’t have spiritual intimacy and sincerity. People in whose horoscopes this element is expressed have inner power, imaginative thinking, and sensitivity. When a whole emotional storm occurs inside them, they don’t show it outside. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe people of the Water Trigon do not forget to take care of themselves and their loved ones. They value family values and comfort. Their power is to contact the outside world, and their weakness is excessive impressionability and spiritual instability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"cancer\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":282,\"dislikes\":19},{\"id\":81,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Cancer and Capricorn form the connection of the \\\"family-career.\\\" If home and comfort are important for the first one, for the other one, work and social status are in privileges. Cancer is a romantic by nature: he loves nature, is inspired by art, and is attentive to people around him. He may not understand the cold behavior of Capricorn, who also seems to be more practical. However, even such relations have a future, if the zones of influence in the pair are correctly divided.</p>\",\"sign\":\"cancer\",\"signs\":[\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":413,\"dislikes\":51},{\"id\":82,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Aries attracts Leo with its charisma and self-confidence. Representatives of these zodiac signs have bright personalities, ambitions, and determination that are why they have such an exciting connection. These two signs will support each other in any circumstances. \\r\\n\\r\\nWhen Leo and Sagittarius are meeting, they at once can realize that they are real soul mates. They both are fire signs, and it helps them in relationships.\\r\\n\\r\\nLeo and Libra can build perfect long-term relationships and stay with each other until the end of their lives.</p>\",\"sign\":\"leo\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"libra\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":797,\"dislikes\":100},{\"id\":83,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Leo\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Sagittarius have a passionate and intoxicating relationship. This funny and explosive couple can share bright emotions not only with each other but also with the surrounding people. Both are representatives of the fire element. They understand each other at a deep level, which helps them to get along well in any circumstances.</p>\",\"sign\":\"leo\",\"signs\":[\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":828,\"dislikes\":105},{\"id\":84,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\" Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Dreamers – Leo and Sagittarius – have all chances to become a bright and passionate couple. Both are representatives of the fire element, therefore they understand each other at a deep level.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf Leo needs attention and care, Leo should start a relationship with Gemini. There will be a lot of warmth and comfort in this couple. \\r\\n\\r\\nAries and Leo are excellent life partners who will be devoted to each other in any circumstances.</p>\",\"sign\":\"leo\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"gemini\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":535,\"dislikes\":62},{\"id\":85,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The Fire element represents energy, power, and life. It makes you move forward and stand your ground. Those who have a trigon of the Fire element in their horoscopes are confident, fearless, and have a versatile mind. They are enterprising and have excellent managerial skills. Their extraordinary energy helps them achieve their goals.</p>\",\"sign\":\"leo\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"leo\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":296,\"dislikes\":18},{\"id\":86,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Aquarius love to have an active social life, but they see it differently. Together these zodiac signs make up the balance \\\"personality-community.\\\" Creative self-expression and the ability to show oneself are important for Leo, and Aquarius values freedom and society of equals. Mutual understanding does not immediately arise in this couple, but the passion for parties and events becomes a unifying factor.</p>\",\"sign\":\"leo\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":497,\"dislikes\":74},{\"id\":87,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Personal development and self-improvement are important for Virgo. People with this zodiac sign do not allow emotions to take possession of them. It is not a surprise that Virgo easily approaches Taurus – both are trying to get meaningful and practical relationships.\\r\\nThey can also get a magic connection with Pisces and Capricorn. </p>\",\"sign\":\"virgo\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"taurus\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":898,\"dislikes\":120},{\"id\":88,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Virgo\",\"description\":\"<p>Both of these zodiac signs belong to the elements of the Earth, so their relationship is easy and calm. There are trust, sincerity, and mutual understanding in this couple. The partners are truly loyal to each other that allow them to build strong and serious relationships.</p>\",\"sign\":\"virgo\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":762,\"dislikes\":141},{\"id\":89,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Both zodiac signs – Taurus and Virgo – belong to the elements of the Earth, so their relationship is easy and calm. There are trust, sincerity, and mutual understanding in this couple. The partners are truly loyal to each other that allow them to build strong and serious relationships.\\r\\n\\r\\nCapricorn and Virgo are not only a harmonious couple but also excellent business partners. They have the same ideas about many questions, so they can trust each other completely.</p>\",\"sign\":\"virgo\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":526,\"dislikes\":66},{\"id\":90,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>People whose horoscopes are expressed by the elements of the Earth normally have a practical approach to life. They are prudent, patient, and self-confident personalities. Earth analyzes, structures, and creates the foundation for the next actions. The people of this trigon set real goals and firmly go to them. Although they are careful and attentive, they can defend their interests, if necessary. The main principle of the Earth's trigon is stability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"virgo\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"virgo\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":302,\"dislikes\":23},{\"id\":91,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Mutual understanding in such a couple does not come immediately. Spirituality and inner experiences are important for Pisces, while the Virgo is responsible for practical and rational decisions. Their interests lie in different spheres, which can become an obstacle to creating strong relations.</p>\",\"sign\":\"virgo\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":442,\"dislikes\":59},{\"id\":92,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Libra never agrees on random people. It is important for them to see an intelligent and confident person near them. As an air sign of the Zodiac, Libra tries to get new experience and knowledge. That is why they will be very comfortable with Gemini. They may be interested in different things and sharing ideas together. \\r\\n\\r\\nAquarius and Libra have a common interest in active social life, so they are looking for new friends and trying to express themselves in society. \\r\\n\\r\\nSagittarius also has the potential to become a soul mate for Libra. This couple will have a healthy and positive relationship.</p>\",\"sign\":\"libra\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"gemini\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":817,\"dislikes\":106},{\"id\":93,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Libra\",\"description\":\"<p>There is a powerful intellectual connection between Libra and Gemini. Both signs belong to the elements of Air that allows them to understand each other's psychology. This couple is valued for calm and comfort. They may be interested in different things and sharing common ideas.</p>\",\"sign\":\"libra\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":558,\"dislikes\":157},{\"id\":94,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>There is no more suitable zodiac sign for Libra than Gemini. Each of the partners in this couple will be able to feel special and loved. This is a balanced, understandable, and comfortable relationship with a tremendous future perspective. Both signs belong to the elements of Air that allows them to understand each other's psychology. They may be interested in different things, sharing common ideas, and build plans for the future.</p>\",\"sign\":\"libra\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":425,\"dislikes\":83},{\"id\":95,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The element of Air is considered to be the trigon of ideas and intelligence. People who belong to this element are constantly in search of new knowledge and sensations. The element of Air carries in itself a changing creative activity, giving to people such qualities as flexibility, liveliness, mobility of the mind and psycho, and insatiability. They do not like monotony since it depresses their psycho. The basic principles of a trigon are interconnection and exchange.</p>\",\"sign\":\"libra\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"gemini\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":309,\"dislikes\":20},{\"id\":96,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Fire needs oxygen to burn. Same here: the Fire element meets the Air forming a dangerous, yet intriguing, connection. Aries often make impulsive decisions that lead to unexpected consequences. Libra, on the contrary, have a calm and balanced personality and tend to spend hours making plans. So such relationships can lead to endless fights and disagreements. However, let’s not forget that opposites attract. If a hot-tempered Aries and a tactful Libra find the way to balance each other out, this kind of relationship may become exciting and appealing for both of them!</p>\",\"sign\":\"libra\",\"signs\":[\"aries\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":510,\"dislikes\":57},{\"id\":97,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Scorpio most often does not show his feelings, but at the same time has a strong intuition and easily finds people close in spirit. Relations with this zodiac sign are often very harmonious if it is possible to find a common language with Scorpio. Cancer has all possibilities to get an important place in the life of Scorpio because both of them appreciate emotional security and calm. A wonderful relationship can be created with Capricorn too, as partners will be eager to support each other in everything. Taurus is the opposite sign for Scorpio. Such a union can have a future if everyone takes on obligations and responsibilities in this couple.</p>\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"cancer\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":669,\"dislikes\":118},{\"id\":98,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Scorpio\",\"description\":\"<p>Two signs of Water element – Cancer and Scorpio – know how to save a trustful relationship. This is the perfect couple in all meanings. They share similar interests, care about each other, build inspirational plans, and make them true.</p>\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":731,\"dislikes\":129},{\"id\":100,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>As an element of Water, Scorpio can be quite restrained and calm. It will be easy for him to reveal emotions and feelings together with Capricorn.\\r\\nIn the relationship between Cancer and Scorpio there will be less passion, but more mutual understanding and trust, because both of them appreciate emotional security and calm.\\r\\nYou get a fantastic alliance with Pisces! Love chemistry will truly work for this couple.</p>\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"cancer\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":559,\"dislikes\":71},{\"id\":101,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>Water is considered the trigon of sensations and feelings. Representatives of the water element have a strong connection with the unconscious mind. They are not interested in empty talking, which doesn’t have spiritual intimacy and sincerity. People in whose horoscopes this element is expressed have inner power, imaginative thinking, and sensitivity. When a whole emotional storm occurs inside them, they don’t show it outside. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe people of the Water Trigon do not forget to take care of themselves and their loved ones. They value family values and comfort. Their power is to contact the outside world, and their weakness is excessive impressionability and spiritual instability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":292,\"dislikes\":20},{\"id\":102,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Each zodiac sign belongs to one of four elements: Water, Air, Earth, and Fire. If the partner has the same trigon with you, then such a relationship can be easy and pleasant. But, if it is the opposite sign of the zodiac, you may feel uncomfortable.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are passion and emotions in a relation between Taurus and Scorpio. Both partners are jealous and often try to destroy each other's independence. Taurus will not have a scandal without good reason, because it prefers a calm and comfortable life. But Scorpio, whose mood changes all the time, will definitely try to find an excuse to do it. </p>\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":353,\"dislikes\":47},{\"id\":103,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Sagittarius isn’t greedy to show its emotions and feelings. If it likes someone, it is immediately noticeable. Sagittarius is generous in relationships and able to see only good in others. Sagittarius is attracted by fearless personalities; therefore Aries is an ideal candidate. Fire sign Leo is also an excellent partner, which will provide an opportunity to feel stability in a relationship. You can count on respect for personal boundaries and a sense of independence in relations with Libra.</p>\",\"sign\":\"sagittarius\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"leo\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":875,\"dislikes\":90},{\"id\":104,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Sagittarius\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Sagittarius have a passionate and intoxicating relationship. This funny and explosive couple can share bright emotions not only with each other but also with the surrounding people. Both are representatives of the fire element. They understand each other at a deep level, which helps them to get along well in any circumstances.</p>\",\"sign\":\"sagittarius\",\"signs\":[\"leo\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":685,\"dislikes\":106},{\"id\":105,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Sagittarius have a passionate and intoxicating relationship. This funny and explosive couple can share bright emotions not only with each other but also with the surrounding people. Both are representatives of the fire element. They understand each other at a deep level, which helps them to get along well in any circumstances. But you should be careful: you will always feel the spirit of competition with Leo. Aquarius will help to cool the passions. A more calm and balanced relationship will be managed with it.</p>\",\"sign\":\"sagittarius\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"leo\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":415,\"dislikes\":67},{\"id\":106,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The element of fire is energy, strength, and life. It forces you to go forward and uphold your beliefs. People whose horoscopes there is trigon of the elements of Fire have a flexible mind, self-confidence, and courage. They possess managerial abilities and enterprise. Their extraordinary energy helps to achieve their desired goals. The principle of the element of Fire is the desire for movement.</p>\",\"sign\":\"sagittarius\",\"signs\":[\"aries\",\"leo\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":317,\"dislikes\":20},{\"id\":107,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Gemini and Sagittarius have a passion for new knowledge and travel. They are connected by a lively interest in different courses, entertainment, and cultural events. This couple will never get bored while learning and discovering the world.</p>\",\"sign\":\"sagittarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\"],\"element\":\"fire\",\"likes\":543,\"dislikes\":47},{\"id\":108,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Capricorns are cute people who easily captivate. But they try to keep their emotions to themselves, so it’s not always clear what the representatives of this sign really feel. Capricorns are very selective and prefer to plan everything carefully. Professional and social image is important for them, therefore they are looking for partners with similar interests. Based on the aspirations and life values of Capricorn, Cancer is ideal for it. Both of them will find support and mutual understanding in such relationships. All these will help to move towards their goals quickly. Virgo and Taurus are also excellent partners for Capricorn since everyone is united by a rational approach to life.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"cancer\",\"virgo\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":747,\"dislikes\":78},{\"id\":109,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Capricorn\",\"description\":\"<p>Both zodiac signs value emotional stability and practicality. They simply adore each other, and it is difficult not to notice to others. The reason for their strong relationship is that there is sincerity, trust, and love in their union.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":576,\"dislikes\":110},{\"id\":110,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Capricorns like serious and purposeful people. They may not show emotions, but these cute shyness suits them very much. As for the family, Capricorns very rarely make a fast decision in this regard. They do not rush into love “like a whirlpool with their heads”, but practically approach the issue of marriage. Representatives of the zodiac signs of the earth element: Taurus and Virgo will become good partners for Capricorn.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere is a big chance to build a happy relationship with Scorpio too. Capricorn's mind and practicality combined with Scorpio's cunning and insight is a great fuel for a happy union.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"virgo\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":498,\"dislikes\":50},{\"id\":111,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>People whose horoscopes are expressed by the elements of the Earth normally have a practical approach to life. They are prudent, patient, and self-confident personalities. Earth analyzes, structures, and creates the foundation for the next actions. The people of this trigon set real goals and firmly go to them. Although they are careful and attentive, they can defend their interests, if necessary. The main principle of the Earth's trigon is stability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"virgo\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":250,\"dislikes\":18},{\"id\":112,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Cancer and Capricorn form the connection of the \\\"family-career.\\\" If home and comfort are important for the first one, for the other one, work and social status are in privileges. Cancer is a romantic by nature: he loves nature, is inspired by art, and is attentive to people around him. He may not understand the cold behavior of Capricorn, who also seems to be more practical. However, even such relations have a future, if the zones of influence in the pair are correctly divided.</p>\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"earth\",\"likes\":391,\"dislikes\":53},{\"id\":113,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Aquarians are friendly and nice people with a fine mental organization. They have a lively mind and curiosity. Representatives of this zodiac sign easily make new acquaintances, share their original ideas about the world, and they are not afraid to change their usual way of life. They hate the dullness and routine. Aquarius is easily impressed by air signs: it will chat non-stop with Gemini and try to spend as much time as possible with Libra. And it will find another soul mate in an independent and confident Sagittarius.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\",\"libra\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":820,\"dislikes\":89},{\"id\":114,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Aquarius\",\"description\":\"Representatives of the air element – Gemini and Aquarius – understand each other perfectly. This union is built on an incredibly emotional and spiritual connection. From the side, their relationships seem almost mystical, because no one can understand them.\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":643,\"dislikes\":107},{\"id\":115,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>If Aquarius wants to be with someone who really understands this sing, then it needs to turn to the air zodiac signs. The most ideal option is Gemini, with whom Aquarius can count on deep feelings and devotion. Also, Aquarius easily finds many things in common with Sagittarius, as they can share a passion for new adventures. </p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"gemini\",\"sagittarius\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":529,\"dislikes\":54},{\"id\":118,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>The element of Air is considered to be the trigon of ideas and intelligence. People who belong to this element are constantly in search of new knowledge and sensations. The element of Air carries in itself a changing creative activity, giving to people such qualities as flexibility, liveliness, mobility of the mind and psycho, and insatiability. They do not like monotony since it depresses their psycho. The basic principles of a trigon are interconnection and exchange.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"aquarius\",\"gemini\",\"libra\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":301,\"dislikes\":15},{\"id\":119,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Leo and Aquarius love to have an active social life, but they see it differently. Together these zodiac signs make up the balance \\\"personality-community.\\\" Creative self-expression and the ability to show oneself are important for Leo, and Aquarius values freedom and society of equals. Mutual understanding does not immediately arise in this couple, but the passion for parties and events becomes a unifying factor.</p>\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\",\"signs\":[\"leo\"],\"element\":\"air\",\"likes\":468,\"dislikes\":78},{\"id\":120,\"category\":\"friendship\",\"title\":\"Best soulmates\",\"description\":\"<p>Sentimental Pisces are looking for a man who will become their soul mate. And they can build trustful and deep relationships with representatives of two elements: Water and Earth. Since Pisces themselves often soar in the clouds and dream a lot, they need a more practical and down to earth partner. Sagittarius is perfect for this role: he knows a lot about romance, but he is not far away from reality.\\r\\n\\r\\nPisces can have an unusually harmonious relationship with Capricorn. Usually, a spark appears between the representatives of these signs, which forces them to develop communication a lot. The same powerful connection is formed with Cancer: partners literally read each other's thoughts and desires.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"taurus\",\"cancer\",\"capricorn\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":620,\"dislikes\":131},{\"id\":121,\"category\":\"love\",\"title\":\"Best couple for Pisces \",\"description\":\"<p>There is an instant attraction between Cancer and Pisces. Deep mental communication is not easy to eliminate, so these relationships can last a very long time. The fact that both zodiac signs belong to the water element determines the similarity of interests, values, and aspirations. </p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":717,\"dislikes\":97},{\"id\":122,\"category\":\"marriage\",\"title\":\"Best Match for Marriage\",\"description\":\"<p>Natural compatibility is within its element of water: with Cancer and Scorpio. Successful relationships: trust, mutual understanding, spiritual closeness.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":527,\"dislikes\":58},{\"id\":123,\"category\":\"career\",\"title\":\"Matching element signs\",\"description\":\"<p>Water is considered the trigon of sensations and feelings. Representatives of the water element have a strong connection with the unconscious mind. They are not interested in empty talking, which doesn’t have spiritual intimacy and sincerity. People in whose horoscopes this element is expressed have inner power, imaginative thinking, and sensitivity. When a whole emotional storm occurs inside them, they don’t show it outside. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe people of the Water Trigon do not forget to take care of themselves and their loved ones. They value family values and comfort. Their power is to contact the outside world, and their weakness is excessive impressionability and spiritual instability.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"pisces\",\"cancer\",\"scorpio\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":321,\"dislikes\":21},{\"id\":124,\"category\":\"opposite\",\"title\":\"Opposite Sign\",\"description\":\"<p>Mutual understanding in such a couple does not come immediately. Spirituality and inner experiences are important for Pisces, while the Virgo is responsible for practical and rational decisions. Their interests lie in different spheres, which can become an obstacle to creating strong relations.</p>\",\"sign\":\"pisces\",\"signs\":[\"virgo\"],\"element\":\"water\",\"likes\":412,\"dislikes\":64}]"
          },
