          "content": {
            "size": 10109,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"id\":4,\"planet\":\"mercury\",\"tags\":[\"Tech glitches\",\"Miscommunication\",\"Forgetfulness\"],\"description\":\"<p>Mercury rules communication, thinking, learning, travel, and technology. During Mercury retrograde, it's best to review past plans rather than start major new projects. Be patient and double-check all details to avoid miscommunications and delays.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Misunderstandings and arguments\",\"Delays in travel or shipping\",\"Emails or messages getting lost\",\"Tech glitches or data errors\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":16,\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"do\":\"Use this period to revisit creative projects, reconnect with old friends, and dive deep into spiritual practices or journaling.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid signing contracts, overcommitting emotionally, or relying solely on intuition for major decisions.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I reconnect with my intuition?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_16_689c70cdab8f1.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"pisces\"]},{\"id\":19,\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"do\":\"Take time to nurture family connections, revisit memories, and create emotional security through thoughtful reflection and home organization.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid taking things too personally, initiating serious relationship talks, or making big decisions based on nostalgia.\\r\\n\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I better nurture my emotional needs?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_19_689c710a0aa10.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"cancer\"]},{\"id\":22,\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"do\":\"Reflect on past emotional patterns, reassess financial agreements, and focus on inner healing.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid digging up old grudges, making impulsive investments, or engaging in power struggles.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Where in my life do I need to let go of control?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_22_689c718e95e5e.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"scorpio\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"sign\":\"pisces\"},{\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"sign\":\"cancer\"},{\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\"}]},{\"id\":7,\"planet\":\"venus\",\"tags\":[\"Love tension\",\"Financial confusion\",\"Style regrets\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Venus retrograde, past lovers or unresolved emotions may resurface, and it's not the ideal time for cosmetic changes or big financial decisions. Reflect on what (and who) you truly value.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Old loves reappearing\",\"Misunderstandings in relationships\",\"Second-guessing style choices\",\"Unexpected expenses\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":25,\"start\":\"2026-10-03\",\"end\":\"2026-11-14\",\"do\":\"Reconnect with past relationships or creative projects and gather inspiration for new creative projects.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid drastic makeovers, luxury purchases, or cosmetic procedures, or don’t start new romantic relationships.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do my relationships reflect who I really am?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_25_689c7176c39f4.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"libra\",\"scorpio\"]}],\"signs\":[]},{\"id\":10,\"planet\":\"mars\",\"tags\":[\"Low motivation\",\"Frustration\",\"Flashbacks\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Mars retrograde, anger simmers, old conflicts may resurface, and direct action often backfires. Rather than pushing forward, reflect on your goals and how you channel your energy.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Burnout or loss of motivation\",\"Arguments resurfacing\",\"Delays in physical goals\",\"Passive-aggressive behavior\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":34,\"start\":\"2027-01-10\",\"end\":\"2027-04-01\",\"do\":\"Finish an old project, create a painting, write a poem, and recall what you used to love.\",\"dont\":\"Do intense workouts, make impulsive decisions, or engage in heated arguments.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do my daily actions reflect the passion I want to live with?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_34_689c71ba2e78f.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"leo\",\"virgo\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2027-01-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-21\",\"sign\":\"virgo\"},{\"start\":\"2027-02-21\",\"end\":\"2027-04-01\",\"sign\":\"leo\"}]},{\"id\":13,\"planet\":\"jupiter\",\"tags\":[\"Inner reflection\",\"Delays in progress\",\"Rewriting your truth\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Jupiter retrograde, this is a time to reassess your personal philosophy, goals for growth, and what you truly consider meaningful. Instead of chasing more, focus on refining what you already have.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Doubts about long-term plans\",\"Revisit of moral beliefs\",\"Delays in travel or education\",\"Second-guessing decisions\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":37,\"start\":\"2025-11-11\",\"end\":\"2026-03-11\",\"do\":\"Revisit your roots, explore ancestral healing, and create a safe, nourishing space for emotional renewal and self-care.\",\"dont\":\"Ignore gut feelings, rush through emotional growth, or make major real estate or family-related decisions without reflection.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Have I built a life that truly feels like home — within and around me?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_37_689c70b0d01b2.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"cancer\"]},{\"id\":40,\"start\":\"2026-12-13\",\"end\":\"2027-04-13\",\"do\":\"Spend time refining your creative voice, reconnect with inner confidence, and reflect on how you express love, leadership, and joy.\",\"dont\":\"Overdramatize situations, chase attention for the wrong reasons, or make risky decisions in love or career for the sake of image.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"What would it look like to make decisions with heart, not ego?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_40_689c71a3e8ea3.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"leo\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2025-11-11\",\"end\":\"2026-03-11\",\"sign\":\"cancer\"},{\"start\":\"2026-12-13\",\"end\":\"2027-04-13\",\"sign\":\"leo\"}]},{\"id\":16,\"planet\":\"saturn\",\"tags\":[\"Boundaries tested\",\"Discipline redefined\",\"Long-term vision reset\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Saturn retrograde, life's lessons return for revision. Reexamine commitments, boundaries, and long-term responsibilities. Saturn retrograde offers a chance to rewrite the rules you live by.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Revisit past responsibilities\",\"Question career paths\",\"Tests of patience and discipline\",\"Push to define your boundaries\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":46,\"start\":\"2026-07-26\",\"end\":\"2026-12-10\",\"do\":\"Finish long-delayed personal goals, practice patience with new projects, and exercise regularly.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid accountability, force things that aren’t ready, or make quick choices just to feel in control.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Am I building something meaningful right now?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_46_689c7141e9b29.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aries\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-07-26\",\"end\":\"2026-12-10\",\"sign\":\"aries\"}]},{\"id\":19,\"planet\":\"uranus\",\"tags\":[\"Hurried awakening\",\"Inner rebellion\",\"Sudden insights\"],\"description\":\"<p>During Uranus retrograde, the planet of disruption turns inward, triggering inner revolutions, surprise realizations, and a need to break free from outdated systems. Rather than chasing external change, examine where you're resisting necessary transformation within.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Restless or restricted feeling\",\"Desire to break routines\",\"Old patterns resurfacing\",\"Technological or ideological glitches\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":58,\"start\":\"2026-09-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-08\",\"do\":\"Journal, reconnect with forgotten studies and explore new ways to express your truth.\",\"dont\":\"Rush into new contracts, overthink, or neglect your mental health.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Are my thoughts and words truly my own?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_58_689c715c010a7.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"gemini\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-09-10\",\"end\":\"2027-02-08\",\"sign\":\"gemini\"}]},{\"id\":22,\"planet\":\"neptune\",\"tags\":[\"Clouded clarity\",\"Daily illusions\",\"Heightened intuition\"],\"description\":\"<p>When Neptune goes retrograde, disillusionment occurs, fantasies unravel, and truths hidden beneath dreams come to light. It's a time to confront escapism, substance habits, or spiritual bypassing and realign with deeper, more authentic visions.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Realizations about self-delusion\",\"Old dreams reevaluation\",\"Heightened spiritual sensitivity\",\"Feeling ungrounded\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":67,\"start\":\"2026-07-07\",\"end\":\"2026-12-12\",\"do\":\"Spend time alone in nature, reflect on past leadership roles, and work on solo creative projects.\",\"dont\":\"Use independence as an excuse, rush into new roles or identities, or react impulsively.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How flexible is my mind when facing uncertainty?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_67_689c712b5ead5.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aries\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-07-07\",\"end\":\"2026-12-12\",\"sign\":\"aries\"}]},{\"id\":25,\"planet\":\"pluto\",\"tags\":[\"Deep excavation\",\"Power reversals\",\"Shadow confrontations\"],\"description\":\"<p>When Pluto, the planet of transformation and the underworld, turns retrograde, it invites you to dive beneath the surface and face what’s been buried. Shed toxic attachments, confront control issues, and reclaim personal power. Instead of fearing the dark, explore it.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Intensified inner work\",\"Old wounds resurfacing\",\"Shifts in power dynamics\",\"Release of what no longer serves\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":73,\"start\":\"2026-05-06\",\"end\":\"2026-10-16\",\"do\":\"Delete outdated accounts, review who has access to your data, or explore therapy, coaching, or inner work focused on trust issues.\",\"dont\":\"Ghost your friends, quit a community impulsively, or ignore burnout or mental fatigue.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Do I trust my inner compass?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_73_689c70efb09ff.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"aquarius\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-05-06\",\"end\":\"2026-10-16\",\"sign\":\"aquarius\"}]}]"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:50:56.075Z"
      },
      {
        "_connectionId": "6013",
        "cache": {},
        "request": {
          "method": "GET",
          "url": "https://astrology.astroline.app/api/v1/horoscope?horoscope_type=zodiac&sign=capricorn&early=false",
          "httpVersion": "http/2.0",
          "headers": [
            {
              "name": "content-type",
              "value": "application/json; charset=UTF-8"
            },
            {
              "name": "origin",
              "value": "https://app.astroline.today"
            },
            {
              "name": "referer",
              "value": "https://app.astroline.today/"
            },
            {
              "name": "x-platform",
              "value": "web"
            },
            {
              "name": "x-version",
              "value": "5.18.0"
            }
          ],
          "queryString": [
            {
              "name": "horoscope_type",
              "value": "zodiac"
            },
            {
              "name": "sign",
              "value": "capricorn"
            },
            {
              "name": "early",
              "value": "false"
            }
          ],
          "bodySize": 0
        },
        "response": {
          "status": 200,
          "statusText": "",
          "httpVersion": "http/2.0",
          "headers": [
            {
              "name": "content-type",
              "value": "application/json; charset=UTF-8"
            }
          ],
          "content": {
            "size": 15160,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"horoscope\":[{\"time_type\":\"before_yesterday\",\"text\":\"<p>Today, Capricorn, don’t be afraid to take risks. Sure, your caution and meticulous planning are important — especially when it comes to big decisions. But sometimes, taking the plunge is all you need to move forward.</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>You are going to be uncharacteristically aggressive in love today. Your partner is likely to be rather astonished because he / she is used to tender romantic gestures from you. But they will love your new style and will be more than a suitable match for you. Explore different dimensions of your relationship today. You will be pleasantly surprised.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":60,\"text\":\"<p>You may come across any intense situation which will affect your health severely. Try to free yourself of the burden of work in the days to come to avoid feeling over exhausted. Preserve this energy for making a strong comeback. Do not stretch much over a project as it will ultimately lead you to suffer from headaches or general tension.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":70,\"text\":\"<p>You will enjoy working for the next few days at the workplace but do not get into the comfort zone because if you get lethargic, all your hard work will go down the drain and your chances to get promotion may deplete. Keep on striving for more.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Risk\"},{\"time_type\":\"yesterday\",\"text\":\"<p>You might feel inclined to reassess your reasons for clinging to an outdated belief where affairs of the heart are concerned. What might have worked or been appropriate in the past might no longer suit your emotional needs now. Your romantic world is evolving and demanding you evolve with it. Your needs and desires are updating themselves, and this is to be embraced and welcomed, not resented or feared.</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":60,\"text\":\"<p>You might feel inclined to reassess your reasons for clinging to an outdated belief where affairs of the heart are concerned. What might have worked or been appropriate in the past might no longer suit your emotional needs now. Your romantic world is evolving and demanding you evolve with it. Your needs and desires are updating themselves, and this is to be embraced and welcomed, not resented or feared.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":90,\"text\":\"<p>You will be in good health today. It's a good time to do sports activities that you like. You will have many things and many reasons to be happy about. Someone's love and care will boost your energy level.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>Today you will find that you want the input of a professional in the realm of your career. It is better to go with professional advice if you are not sure about your career choices. Make sure you choose a qualified professional so that you don't get unwise advice. You may also find yourself turning to print and online sources for savvy financial tips and guidance for your long-term growth. </p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Needs\"},{\"time_type\":\"today\",\"text\":\"<p>Tread carefully because bosses, parents and VIPs might suddenly overreact or do something you least expect. Stay light on your feet so that you can jump in either direction. Meanwhile, a heart-to-heart talk with a friend or partner might be meaningful for you today.</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":60,\"text\":\"<p>There may be a surprise in store for you if you are involved in a long-distance relationship. One of you is likely to be traveling to see the other today in a much-anticipated reunion. Make the most of the time that you have together today and don't forget to tell your partner anything and everything that is on your mind. </p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>Today you are feeling that your energy level and your self-confidence are quite high. You are ready face the world head on, as well as hit the gym and put in an extra long workout today. You will find that your confidence is evident for all to notice, and notice they will. Bask in all the attention today! </p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>This is the perfect day to hammer out technical solutions at the workplace. Being rigid is not the right way to deal with different issues. You have to open up to face every challenge coming your way. Be more flexible.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Dialogue\"},{\"time_type\":\"tomorrow\",\"text\":\"<p>Parents should be vigilant today because this is an accident-prone day for your kids. Social plans might change. An unexpected invite might come your way. On the other hand, a fun event might be cancelled. If shopping today, don’t go overboard on luxurious elegance, cuz you will be tempted!</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":60,\"text\":\"<p>You will make a new friend today who will be instrumental in paving a way for your future successes. If you are lucky, this person may also turn out to be a great romantic partner for you! Keep your mind open about the possibilities for this relationship. Share your wishes and dreams with this person and see what the future holds for you. </p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>Today you will actually avoid all major hurdles and struggles on the health front. You will generally be feeling quite well, with a high energy level and no major aches or pains. You should take advantage of this fruitful and healthful time and get outside and enjoy life. You will not be in good health forever, so definitely take advantage of these positive days. </p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":90,\"text\":\"<p>Lessons you have learned from your seniors or bosses will guide you in performing better, smarter and faster at work today. You will be busy solving complex issues since you have to shoulder huge responsibilities.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Change\"},{\"time_type\":\"after_tomorrow\",\"text\":\"<p>Make today all about your kids! You'll want to prioritize their progress and take the time to consider new ways to teach them. Don't forget to spoil them with their favorite treats. Show them how proud you are!</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>You will be feeling very emotional today. Both positive and negative emotions crowd your brain today. So, this is not the best time to take any crucial decision regarding your romantic life. However, it is an excellent time for love and romance, especially if you are already in a committed relationship. Single people will find themselves reaching out to anybody who shows even a slight interest.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>You are pretty charged today. Divert the excess energy in keeping yourself fit and fine. Devise a strategy for proper exercise on a regular basis. Make a point to commit yourself to it. You cannot afford to compromise with your health so check your tendency of drifting away from routine tasks.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":40,\"text\":\"<p>Do not try to multitask today, there is a chance that you may commit some mistakes. It’s OK to take things slowly but attempt to do them right so that there are no losses. Try to build a good rapport with the team members around, and it will be easy for you to get the work done.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Parenting\"},{\"time_type\":\"week\",\"text\":\"<p>A practical focus encourages you to look for opportunities that can pave the way to greater success. However, to enjoy these, you’ll need to move out of your comfort zone and be prepared to take on challenges that may seem daunting at first. It will be worth it over the long term. </p><p>Later in the week you'll face an encounter that you might want to keep under wraps for now. There’s no need to say anything until you feel it’s time.</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":60,\"text\":\"<p>It’s a restless start. You’ll want more than you’re getting but you’ll need to stay focused so you can discuss or negotiate matters related to responsibility. You may feel like blasting off on a binge on Thursday and Friday. If you need to get something out of your chest, it may bo not the best time, you may face some misunderstanding from your partner or a person you're falling for.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":70,\"text\":\"<p>This is a good time for meditation as your pineal glands are activated. So use this time for meditation and improve your intuition. Your abdominal area is activated. You will have to be little more careful with your emotional self. It would not be wise to get into any controversies.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>It's the best time to ease your way into the new job, project or position with no pressure or need to reinvent the wheel. However, things could be emotionally intense. Simply do your best and avoid taking anything personally. There are much larger forces at work. This is a good time for any sort of team effort. Work that focuses on improving the lives of others will see you shine.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Success\"},{\"time_type\":\"month\",\"text\":\"<p>On the 10th, you will feel very confident and decisive in communicating with other people. The words you need will come to your mind by themselves, and your conversations will proceed in a very constructive and smooth manner. </p><p>On the 15th, you will want to move away from your usual routine. You will feel like a real rebel, and this time you should not suppress the impulses that seize you. Do not be afraid to take risks - your bold initiatives will bring you extremely rich results. </p><p>On the 21st, the ambitious side of nature will wake up in you. It's time to think about the future and set several serious goals for yourself on the career front. If you have long wanted to achieve an increase or increase, then ask yourself what prerequisites you need to create for this.\\r\\n</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[{\"tag_type_id\":\"love\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>On the 11th, many extremely interesting ideas in your personal life may visit you, but you may not have the courage to translate them into reality. Will you be able to step over your shyness and move away from your usual routine? Go ahead! On the 17th, you will think a lot about your past decisions and actions on the amorous front. You may regret many of them, but you cannot change the past. Therefore, try to drive away these unpleasant memories from yourself and look again with enthusiasm into the future.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"health\",\"percents\":50,\"text\":\"<p>It would help if you took more care of your physical health. Watch out for infections and viruses. Those born in the third decade of the sign should be more careful while driving, and also try to keep aggression and irritation in check. In the second half of the month, you will likely be more susceptible to stress and fatigue. Get more rest. Some men and women of the sign may experience depression. Look for ways to unwind.</p>\"},{\"tag_type_id\":\"career\",\"percents\":80,\"text\":\"<p>This month you will have an excellent opportunity to increase your income and strengthen your financial position. So, already on the 1st, your intuition will drive you, and if you listen to it carefully, it will help you make some very profitable investments. On the 21st, it will be better for you to think twice about all your steps before taking them. Nevertheless, communication with other people will be very successful for you, and they will help you make several rather important decisions.</p>\"}],\"focus\":\"Ambition\"},{\"time_type\":\"year\",\"text\":\"<p>Capricorn, 2026 centers on building a life that can actually hold your long-term plans. With Saturn shaping the year, you’re asked to think less about quick wins and more about the kind of stability that lets you move forward without constantly looking over your shoulder.\\r\\n</p><p>Early transits support practical changes and small upgrades that make your days run more smoothly. As Saturn settles into Aries, attention shifts to your foundations — home, family, emotional security, and the structures you lean on when things get hard. This isn’t about polishing the surface; it’s about reinforcing what’s underneath.\\r\\n</p><p>Late winter and early spring bring a series of “reality check” moments that clarify your limits and your responsibilities. Some plans may need to be simplified, some commitments renegotiated. The more honest you are about what you can truly sustain, the more solid your progress becomes. This is the season for long-range thinking, clear boundaries, and serious choices you won’t regret later.\\r\\n</p><p>From late July, Saturn’s retrograde turns the focus inward. You’re invited to review the routines, promises, and living situations you’ve built so far and notice what actually supports you — and what’s become too tight or too heavy. Adjustments now may not be dramatic, but they’re meaningful.\\r\\n</p><p>By the time Saturn moves direct in December, the ground under your feet feels different: less shaky, more intentional. 2026 may not be loud, but it leaves you with stronger roots, cleaner priorities, and a clearer sense of the life you’re slowly, deliberately climbing toward.\\r\\n</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[],\"focus\":\"Discipline\"},{\"time_type\":\"next_year\",\"text\":\"<p>Capricorn, 2026 centers on building a life that can actually hold your long-term plans. With Saturn shaping the year, you’re asked to think less about quick wins and more about the kind of stability that lets you move forward without constantly looking over your shoulder.\\r\\n</p><p>Early transits support practical changes and small upgrades that make your days run more smoothly. As Saturn settles into Aries, attention shifts to your foundations — home, family, emotional security, and the structures you lean on when things get hard. This isn’t about polishing the surface; it’s about reinforcing what’s underneath.\\r\\n</p><p>Late winter and early spring bring a series of “reality check” moments that clarify your limits and your responsibilities. Some plans may need to be simplified, some commitments renegotiated. The more honest you are about what you can truly sustain, the more solid your progress becomes. This is the season for long-range thinking, clear boundaries, and serious choices you won’t regret later.\\r\\n</p><p>From late July, Saturn’s retrograde turns the focus inward. You’re invited to review the routines, promises, and living situations you’ve built so far and notice what actually supports you — and what’s become too tight or too heavy. Adjustments now may not be dramatic, but they’re meaningful.\\r\\n</p><p>By the time Saturn moves direct in December, the ground under your feet feels different: less shaky, more intentional. 2026 may not be loud, but it leaves you with stronger roots, cleaner priorities, and a clearer sense of the life you’re slowly, deliberately climbing toward.\\r\\n</p>\",\"quality\":\"default\",\"tags\":[],\"focus\":\"Discipline\"}],\"facts\":null,\"horoscope_info\":{\"horoscope_type\":\"zodiac\",\"sign\":\"capricorn\"}}"
          },
          "redirectURL": "",
          "bodySize": -1
        },
        "startedDateTime": "2026-02-28T04:50:56.087Z"
      },
