          "content": {
            "size": 2227,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"id\":4,\"planet\":\"mercury\",\"tags\":[\"Tech glitches\",\"Miscommunication\",\"Forgetfulness\"],\"description\":\"<p>Mercury rules communication, thinking, learning, travel, and technology. During Mercury retrograde, it's best to review past plans rather than start major new projects. Be patient and double-check all details to avoid miscommunications and delays.</p>\\r\\n\",\"expect\":[\"Misunderstandings and arguments\",\"Delays in travel or shipping\",\"Emails or messages getting lost\",\"Tech glitches or data errors\"],\"retrogrades\":[{\"id\":16,\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"do\":\"Use this period to revisit creative projects, reconnect with old friends, and dive deep into spiritual practices or journaling.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid signing contracts, overcommitting emotionally, or relying solely on intuition for major decisions.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I reconnect with my intuition?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_16_689c70cdab8f1.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"pisces\"]},{\"id\":19,\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"do\":\"Take time to nurture family connections, revisit memories, and create emotional security through thoughtful reflection and home organization.\\r\\n\",\"dont\":\"Avoid taking things too personally, initiating serious relationship talks, or making big decisions based on nostalgia.\\r\\n\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"How can I better nurture my emotional needs?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_19_689c710a0aa10.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"cancer\"]},{\"id\":22,\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"do\":\"Reflect on past emotional patterns, reassess financial agreements, and focus on inner healing.\",\"dont\":\"Avoid digging up old grudges, making impulsive investments, or engaging in power struggles.\",\"reflection\":{\"text\":\"Where in my life do I need to let go of control?\",\"image_url\":\"https://astroline.fsn1.your-objectstorage.com/uploads/retrograde_periods/period_22_689c718e95e5e.webp\"},\"zodiac_signs\":[\"scorpio\"]}],\"signs\":[{\"start\":\"2026-02-25\",\"end\":\"2026-03-20\",\"sign\":\"pisces\"},{\"start\":\"2026-06-29\",\"end\":\"2026-07-23\",\"sign\":\"cancer\"},{\"start\":\"2026-10-24\",\"end\":\"2026-11-13\",\"sign\":\"scorpio\"}]}"
